WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.570 --> 00:00:06.570

2
00:00:07.570 --> 00:00:10.570

3
00:00:37.570 --> 00:00:41.570
<font color="#787878">These are dark times, 
there is no denying.</font>

4
00:00:41.570 --> 00:00:47.570
<font color="#787878">Our world has, perhaps,
faced no greater threat than it does today.</font>

5
00:00:48.570 --> 00:00:52.570
<font color="#787878">But I say this to our citizenry:</font>

6
00:00:52.604 --> 00:00:56.506
<font color="#787878">We, ever your servants....</font>

7
00:00:56.675 --> 00:00:59.337
<font color="#787878">....will continue to defend your liberty....</font>

8
00:00:59.511 --> 00:01:03.845
<font color="#787878">....and repel the forces
that seek to take it from you.</font>

9
00:01:05.050 --> 00:01:10.317
<font color="#787878">Your Ministry remains....</font>

10
00:01:10.855 --> 00:01:12.823
<font color="#787878">....strong.</font>

11
00:01:30.175 --> 00:01:32.370
<font color="#787878">Hermione. Tea's ready, darling.</font>

12
00:01:32.544 --> 00:01:34.478
<font color="#787878">Coming, Mom.</font>

13
00:01:38.416 --> 00:01:40.316
<font color="#787878">Come on, Dudley, hurry up.</font>

14
00:01:40.485 --> 00:01:43.511
<font color="#787878">I still don't understand
why we have to leave.</font>

15
00:01:43.688 --> 00:01:48.455
<font color="#787878">Because, unh,
it's not safe for us here anymore.</font>

16
00:02:03.842 --> 00:02:08.211
<font color="#787878">Ron, tell your father
supper's nearly ready.</font>

17
00:02:13.218 --> 00:02:14.947
<font color="#787878">Is this in Australia?</font>

18
00:02:15.120 --> 00:02:17.088
<font color="#787878">Looks wonderful, doesn't it?</font>

19
00:02:17.255 --> 00:02:22.124
<font color="#787878">Three and a half thousand
kilometers along Australia's east coast.</font>

20
00:02:23.428 --> 00:02:24.952
<font color="#787878">Obliviate.</font>

21
00:04:39.297 --> 00:04:40.958
<font color="#787878">Severus.</font>

22
00:04:41.132 --> 00:04:44.499
<font color="#787878">I was beginning to worry
you had lost your way.</font>

23
00:04:44.669 --> 00:04:48.127
<font color="#787878">Come, we've saved you a seat.</font>

24
00:04:52.577 --> 00:04:53.908
<font color="#787878">You bring news, I trust?</font>

25
00:04:54.078 --> 00:04:57.741
<font color="#787878">It will happen Saturday next, at nightfall.</font>

26
00:04:57.916 --> 00:05:00.282
<font color="#787878">I've heard differently, my Lord.</font>

27
00:05:00.451 --> 00:05:03.579
<font color="#787878">Dawlish, the Auror,
has let slip that the Potter boy....</font>

28
00:05:03.755 --> 00:05:06.849
<font color="#787878">....will not be moved
until the 30th of this month.</font>

29
00:05:07.292 --> 00:05:08.554
<font color="#787878">The day before he turns 17.</font>

30
00:05:08.726 --> 00:05:11.957
<font color="#787878">This is a false trail.</font>

31
00:05:12.630 --> 00:05:16.794
<font color="#787878">The Auror Office no longer plays any part in the protection of Harry Potter.</font>

32
00:05:16.968 --> 00:05:21.337
<font color="#787878">Those closest to him believe we have infiltrated the Ministry.</font>

33
00:05:21.940 --> 00:05:23.532
<font color="#787878">Well, they got that right, haven't they?</font>

34
00:05:28.012 --> 00:05:30.480
<font color="#787878">What say you, Pius?</font>

35
00:05:34.018 --> 00:05:36.612
<font color="#787878">One hears many things, my Lord.</font>

36
00:05:36.788 --> 00:05:39.348
<font color="#787878">Whether the truth is among them is not clear.</font>

37
00:05:39.524 --> 00:05:42.891
<font color="#787878">Heh. Spoken like a true politician.</font>

38
00:05:43.061 --> 00:05:46.121
<font color="#787878">You will, I think,
prove most useful, Pius.</font>

39
00:05:49.734 --> 00:05:52.965
<font color="#787878">~ Where will he be taken, the boy?
~ To a safe house.</font>

40
00:05:53.371 --> 00:05:55.999
<font color="#787878">Most likely the home of someone in the Order.</font>

41
00:05:56.174 --> 00:05:59.405
<font color="#787878">I'm told it's been given
every manner of protection possible.</font>

42
00:05:59.577 --> 00:06:03.172
<font color="#787878">Once there,
it will be impractical to attack him.</font>

43
00:06:03.348 --> 00:06:08.285
<font color="#787878">Ahem. My Lord.
I'd like to volunteer myself for this task.</font>

44
00:06:08.453 --> 00:06:09.442
<font color="#787878">I want to kill the boy.</font>

45
00:06:10.788 --> 00:06:12.016
<font color="#787878">Wormtail!</font>

46
00:06:12.190 --> 00:06:15.159
<font color="#787878">Have I not spoken to you
about keeping our guest quiet?</font>

47
00:06:15.326 --> 00:06:17.226
<font color="#787878">Yes, my Lord.</font>

48
00:06:17.395 --> 00:06:20.057
<font color="#787878">Right away, my Lord.</font>

49
00:06:20.298 --> 00:06:24.792
<font color="#787878">As inspiring
as I find your bloodlust, Bellatrix....</font>

50
00:06:25.236 --> 00:06:28.535
<font color="#787878">....I must be the one to kill Harry Potter.</font>

51
00:06:31.009 --> 00:06:35.810
<font color="#787878">But I face an unfortunate complication.</font>

52
00:06:35.980 --> 00:06:41.179
<font color="#787878">That my wand and Potter's
share the same core.</font>

53
00:06:42.420 --> 00:06:48.984
<font color="#787878">They are, in some ways, twins.</font>

54
00:06:49.160 --> 00:06:53.859
<font color="#787878">We can wound,
but not fatally harm one another.</font>

55
00:06:55.466 --> 00:06:58.264
<font color="#787878">If I am to kill him....</font>

56
00:06:58.937 --> 00:07:02.703
<font color="#787878">....I must do it with another's wand.</font>

57
00:07:04.709 --> 00:07:10.409
<font color="#787878">Come,
surely one of you would like the honor?</font>

58
00:07:12.016 --> 00:07:13.677
<font color="#787878">Mm?</font>

59
00:07:15.386 --> 00:07:20.187
<font color="#787878">What about you, Lucius?</font>

60
00:07:22.694 --> 00:07:24.093
<font color="#787878">My Lord?</font>

61
00:07:24.262 --> 00:07:26.230
<font color="#787878">"My Lord?"</font>

62
00:07:27.298 --> 00:07:30.927
<font color="#787878">I require your wand.</font>

63
00:07:44.248 --> 00:07:46.716
<font color="#787878">Do I detect elm?</font>

64
00:07:46.884 --> 00:07:48.852
<font color="#787878">Yes, my Lord.</font>

65
00:07:54.792 --> 00:07:57.727
<font color="#787878">And the core?</font>

66
00:07:57.895 --> 00:08:00.090
<font color="#787878">Dragon. Ahem.</font>

67
00:08:00.264 --> 00:08:01.891
<font color="#787878">Dragon heartstring, my Lord.</font>

68
00:08:02.066 --> 00:08:04.261
<font color="#787878">~ Dragon heartstring.
~ Mm.</font>

69
00:08:19.984 --> 00:08:21.747
<font color="#787878">To those of you who do not know....</font>

70
00:08:21.919 --> 00:08:24.581
<font color="#787878">....we are joined tonight
by Miss Charity Burbage....</font>

71
00:08:24.756 --> 00:08:30.251
<font color="#787878">....who, until recently, taught at Hogwarts School of Witchcraft and Wizardry.</font>

72
00:08:30.428 --> 00:08:33.886
<font color="#787878">Her specialty was Muggle Studies.</font>

73
00:08:37.101 --> 00:08:43.370
<font color="#787878">It is Miss Burbage's belief that Muggles are not so different from us.</font>

74
00:08:43.541 --> 00:08:47.170
<font color="#787878">She would, given her way....</font>

75
00:08:47.945 --> 00:08:49.879
<font color="#787878">....have us mate with them.</font>

76
00:08:53.551 --> 00:08:59.751
<font color="#787878">To her, the mixture of magical and Muggle blood is not an abomination....</font>

77
00:08:59.924 --> 00:09:02.950
<font color="#787878">....but something to be encouraged.</font>

78
00:09:04.028 --> 00:09:05.893
<font color="#787878">Severus.</font>

79
00:09:06.064 --> 00:09:08.032
<font color="#787878">Severus, please.</font>

80
00:09:09.700 --> 00:09:11.861
<font color="#787878">We're friends.</font>

81
00:09:16.641 --> 00:09:18.199
<font color="#787878">Avada Kedavra!</font>

82
00:09:28.453 --> 00:09:30.478
<font color="#787878">Nagini.</font>

83
00:09:34.092 --> 00:09:35.753
<font color="#787878">Dinner.</font>

84
00:11:21.065 --> 00:11:24.466
<font color="#787878">~ Hello, Harry.
~ All right. Wow.</font>

85
00:11:24.635 --> 00:11:25.727
<font color="#787878">Hello.</font>

86
00:11:25.903 --> 00:11:28.804
<font color="#787878">~ You're looking fit.
~ Yeah, he's absolutely gorgeous.</font>

87
00:11:28.973 --> 00:11:31.441
<font color="#787878">What say we get undercover
before someone murders him?</font>

88
00:11:31.609 --> 00:11:32.633
<font color="#787878">Evening.</font>

89
00:11:37.548 --> 00:11:39.948
<font color="#787878">I thought you were
looking after the Prime Minister.</font>

90
00:11:40.117 --> 00:11:42.017
<font color="#787878">You are more important.</font>

91
00:11:42.186 --> 00:11:45.246
<font color="#787878">~ Hello, Harry. Bill Weasley.
~ Oh. Pleasure to meet you.</font>

92
00:11:45.423 --> 00:11:48.415
<font color="#787878">~ He was never always this handsome.
~ Dead ugly.</font>

93
00:11:48.593 --> 00:11:49.992
<font color="#787878">True enough.</font>

94
00:11:50.161 --> 00:11:52.686
<font color="#787878">Owe it all to a werewolf,
name of Greyback.</font>

95
00:11:52.863 --> 00:11:56.230
<font color="#787878">~ Hope to repay the favor one day.
~ You're still beautiful to me, William.</font>

96
00:11:56.601 --> 00:12:00.230
<font color="#787878">Just remember, Fleur,
Bill takes his steaks on the raw side now.</font>

97
00:12:00.404 --> 00:12:02.736
<font color="#787878">My husband, the joker.</font>

98
00:12:02.907 --> 00:12:06.172
<font color="#787878">By the way, wait till you hear the news. Remus and I--</font>

99
00:12:06.344 --> 00:12:08.778
<font color="#787878">All right. We'll have time
for a cozy catch-up later.</font>

100
00:12:08.946 --> 00:12:11.915
<font color="#787878">We've got to get the hell out of here. And soon.</font>

101
00:12:12.583 --> 00:12:15.848
<font color="#787878">Potter, you're underage, which means you've still got the Trace on you.</font>

102
00:12:16.020 --> 00:12:17.044
<font color="#787878">What's the Trace?</font>

103
00:12:17.221 --> 00:12:19.883
<font color="#787878">If you sneeze, the Ministry will know who wipes your nose.</font>

104
00:12:20.057 --> 00:12:23.220
<font color="#787878">We have to use those means of transport the Trace can't detect:</font>

105
00:12:23.394 --> 00:12:25.726
<font color="#787878">Brooms, Thestrals and the like. We go in pairs.</font>

106
00:12:25.896 --> 00:12:29.662
<font color="#787878">That way, if anyone's out there waiting for us, and I reckon there will be....</font>

107
00:12:29.834 --> 00:12:32.325
<font color="#787878">....they won't know which Harry Potter is the real one.</font>

108
00:12:32.770 --> 00:12:33.930
<font color="#787878">The real one?</font>

109
00:12:35.273 --> 00:12:38.367
<font color="#787878">I believe you're familiar
with this particular brew.</font>

110
00:12:38.542 --> 00:12:40.840
<font color="#787878">No. Absolutely not.</font>

111
00:12:41.012 --> 00:12:42.343
<font color="#787878">I told you he'd take it well.</font>

112
00:12:42.513 --> 00:12:45.641
<font color="#787878">No, if you think I'm gonna let everyone risk their lives for me, I--</font>

113
00:12:45.816 --> 00:12:48.876
<font color="#787878">~ Never done that before, have we?
~ No. No. This is different.</font>

114
00:12:49.053 --> 00:12:51.044
<font color="#787878">I mean, taking that, becoming me. No.</font>

115
00:12:51.222 --> 00:12:53.053
<font color="#787878">Well, none of us really fancy it, mate.</font>

116
00:12:53.224 --> 00:12:57.388
<font color="#787878">Imagine if something went wrong, and we ended up a scrawny, specky git forever.</font>

117
00:12:57.561 --> 00:12:59.222
<font color="#787878">Everyone here is of age, Potter.</font>

118
00:12:59.930 --> 00:13:01.363
<font color="#787878">They've all agreed to take the risk.</font>

119
00:13:02.733 --> 00:13:05.634
<font color="#787878">Technically, I've been coerced.</font>

120
00:13:05.803 --> 00:13:07.998
<font color="#787878">Mundungus Fletcher, Mr. Potter.</font>

121
00:13:08.172 --> 00:13:10.732
<font color="#787878">~ Always been a huge admirer.
~ Nip it, Mundungus.</font>

122
00:13:12.043 --> 00:13:14.534
<font color="#787878">All right, Granger, as discussed.</font>

123
00:13:14.712 --> 00:13:17.442
<font color="#787878">~ Blimey, Hermione.
~ Straight in here, if you please.</font>

124
00:13:27.291 --> 00:13:31.489
<font color="#787878">For those of you who haven't taken Polyjuice Potion before, fair warning:</font>

125
00:13:31.662 --> 00:13:33.289
<font color="#787878">It tastes like goblin piss.</font>

126
00:13:33.464 --> 00:13:36.433
<font color="#787878">Have a lot of experiences with that, do you, Mad-Eye?</font>

127
00:13:37.335 --> 00:13:40.270
<font color="#787878">Just trying to diffuse the tension.</font>

128
00:13:41.305 --> 00:13:43.102
<font color="#787878">Oh.</font>

129
00:13:46.177 --> 00:13:47.940
<font color="#787878">Ugh.</font>

130
00:14:12.203 --> 00:14:14.262
<font color="#787878">Wow, we're identical.</font>

131
00:14:14.438 --> 00:14:15.496
<font color="#787878">Not yet, you're not.</font>

132
00:14:19.176 --> 00:14:21.736
<font color="#787878">Haven't got anything
a bit more sporting, have you?</font>

133
00:14:21.912 --> 00:14:23.379
<font color="#787878">I don't really fancy this color.</font>

134
00:14:23.547 --> 00:14:26.345
<font color="#787878">Well, fancy this, you're not you. So shut it and strip.</font>

135
00:14:26.517 --> 00:14:28.075
<font color="#787878">All right, all right.</font>

136
00:14:28.252 --> 00:14:29.810
<font color="#787878">You'll need to change too, Potter.</font>

137
00:14:30.321 --> 00:14:32.949
<font color="#787878">Bill, look away. I'm hideous.</font>

138
00:14:33.124 --> 00:14:35.422
<font color="#787878">I knew she was lying about that tattoo.</font>

139
00:14:35.593 --> 00:14:38.027
<font color="#787878">Harry, your eyesight really is awful.</font>

140
00:14:38.195 --> 00:14:41.892
<font color="#787878">Right, then. We'll be pairing off. Each Potter will have a protector.</font>

141
00:14:42.066 --> 00:14:45.365
<font color="#787878">Mundungus, stick tight to me. I wanna keep an eye on you.</font>

142
00:14:45.903 --> 00:14:47.734
<font color="#787878">~ As for Harry--
~ Yes?</font>

143
00:14:48.572 --> 00:14:49.971
<font color="#787878">The real Harry.</font>

144
00:14:50.141 --> 00:14:52.507
<font color="#787878">~ Where the devil are you, anyway?
~ Here.</font>

145
00:14:52.676 --> 00:14:54.644
<font color="#787878">You'll ride with Hagrid.</font>

146
00:14:54.812 --> 00:14:59.840
<font color="#787878">I brought you here 16 years ago when you were no bigger than a Bowtruckle.</font>

147
00:15:00.017 --> 00:15:02.918
<font color="#787878">Seems only right that I should be the one to take you away now.</font>

148
00:15:03.087 --> 00:15:06.022
<font color="#787878">Yes, it's all very touching. Let's go.</font>

149
00:15:19.336 --> 00:15:23.238
<font color="#787878">Head for the Burrows.
We'll rendezvous there.</font>

150
00:15:23.774 --> 00:15:25.833
<font color="#787878">On the count of three.</font>

151
00:15:26.010 --> 00:15:27.739
<font color="#787878">Hold tight, Harry.</font>

152
00:15:27.912 --> 00:15:29.709
<font color="#787878">One....</font>

153
00:15:30.581 --> 00:15:32.378
<font color="#787878">....two....</font>

154
00:15:38.789 --> 00:15:40.586
<font color="#787878">....three!</font>

155
00:16:10.588 --> 00:16:13.751
<font color="#787878">~ Which one?
~ Where are you?</font>

156
00:16:14.959 --> 00:16:16.688
<font color="#787878">He's on your right!</font>

157
00:16:16.861 --> 00:16:18.488
<font color="#787878">He's over there!</font>

158
00:16:18.662 --> 00:16:20.323
<font color="#787878">Down!</font>

159
00:16:25.803 --> 00:16:27.464
<font color="#787878">Hagrid, we have to help the others!</font>

160
00:16:27.872 --> 00:16:30.773
<font color="#787878">I can't do that, Harry. Mad-Eye's orders.</font>

161
00:16:37.715 --> 00:16:39.512
<font color="#787878">Hang on.</font>

162
00:16:43.320 --> 00:16:45.379
<font color="#787878">Stupefy!</font>

163
00:16:59.103 --> 00:17:00.195
<font color="#787878">Hang on, Harry.</font>

164
00:17:10.114 --> 00:17:11.979
<font color="#787878">Hagrid.</font>

165
00:17:29.199 --> 00:17:31.463
<font color="#787878">No. No.</font>

166
00:17:53.557 --> 00:17:55.548
<font color="#787878">Harry.</font>

167
00:19:15.506 --> 00:19:18.566
<font color="#787878">Harry. Hagrid.</font>

168
00:19:19.977 --> 00:19:23.435
<font color="#787878">What happened? Where are the others?</font>

169
00:19:23.614 --> 00:19:24.774
<font color="#787878">Is no one else back?</font>

170
00:19:24.948 --> 00:19:28.509
<font color="#787878">They were on us right from
the start, Molly. We didn't stand a chance.</font>

171
00:19:28.686 --> 00:19:31.849
<font color="#787878">Well, thank goodness
you two are all right.</font>

172
00:19:32.022 --> 00:19:34.582
<font color="#787878">The Death Eaters were
waiting for us. It was an ambush.</font>

173
00:19:34.758 --> 00:19:37.158
<font color="#787878">Ron and Tonks
should've already been back.</font>

174
00:19:37.327 --> 00:19:38.521
<font color="#787878">Dad and Fred as well.</font>

175
00:19:41.465 --> 00:19:43.126
<font color="#787878">Here!</font>

176
00:19:43.767 --> 00:19:47.203
<font color="#787878">Quick. Into the house.</font>

177
00:19:50.874 --> 00:19:52.933
<font color="#787878">Oh, my boy.</font>

178
00:19:55.112 --> 00:19:57.603
<font color="#787878">Oh. Oh.</font>

179
00:19:59.216 --> 00:20:00.513
<font color="#787878">~ Lupin!
~ What are you doing?</font>

180
00:20:03.053 --> 00:20:05.988
<font color="#787878">What creature sat in the corner....</font>

181
00:20:06.156 --> 00:20:09.455
<font color="#787878">....the first time Harry Potter visited my office in Hogwarts?</font>

182
00:20:09.626 --> 00:20:11.253
<font color="#787878">~ Are you mad?
~ What creature?!</font>

183
00:20:11.428 --> 00:20:13.259
<font color="#787878">A Grindylow.</font>

184
00:20:19.603 --> 00:20:21.264
<font color="#787878">We've been betrayed.</font>

185
00:20:21.438 --> 00:20:23.838
<font color="#787878">Voldemort knew
you were being moved tonight.</font>

186
00:20:24.007 --> 00:20:26.908
<font color="#787878">I had to make sure
you weren't an impostor.</font>

187
00:20:34.051 --> 00:20:35.484
<font color="#787878">Wait.</font>

188
00:20:38.489 --> 00:20:43.017
<font color="#787878">The last words Albus Dumbledore spoke to the pair of us?</font>

189
00:20:44.828 --> 00:20:49.197
<font color="#787878">"Harry is the best hope we have. Trust him."</font>

190
00:20:53.737 --> 00:20:54.829
<font color="#787878">What gave you away?</font>

191
00:20:55.005 --> 00:20:58.202
<font color="#787878">Hedwig, I think.
She was trying to protect me.</font>

192
00:21:14.758 --> 00:21:15.918
<font color="#787878">Thanks.</font>

193
00:21:16.093 --> 00:21:18.254
<font color="#787878">Deserves that. Brilliant, he was.</font>

194
00:21:18.428 --> 00:21:21.522
<font color="#787878">~ I wouldn't be standing here without him.
~ Really?</font>

195
00:21:22.533 --> 00:21:25.195
<font color="#787878">Always the tone of surprise.</font>

196
00:21:33.410 --> 00:21:34.604
<font color="#787878">We the last back?</font>

197
00:21:35.913 --> 00:21:36.937
<font color="#787878">Where's George?</font>

198
00:21:58.235 --> 00:22:00.465
<font color="#787878">How you feeling, Georgie?</font>

199
00:22:02.472 --> 00:22:03.996
<font color="#787878">Saint-like.</font>

200
00:22:05.209 --> 00:22:06.437
<font color="#787878">Come again?</font>

201
00:22:07.377 --> 00:22:10.938
<font color="#787878">Saint-like. I'm holy.</font>

202
00:22:11.448 --> 00:22:14.508
<font color="#787878">I'm holey, Fred. Get it?</font>

203
00:22:16.320 --> 00:22:21.019
<font color="#787878">The whole wide world of ear-related humor and you go for "I'm holey."</font>

204
00:22:21.191 --> 00:22:22.351
<font color="#787878">That's pathetic.</font>

205
00:22:22.960 --> 00:22:25.258
<font color="#787878">Reckon I'm still better-looking than you.</font>

206
00:22:28.799 --> 00:22:30.994
<font color="#787878">Mad-Eye's dead.</font>

207
00:22:41.378 --> 00:22:45.109
<font color="#787878">Mundungus took one look at Voldemort and Disapparated.</font>

208
00:23:08.038 --> 00:23:10.063
<font color="#787878">Head for the Burrows.</font>

209
00:23:10.874 --> 00:23:12.239
<font color="#787878">This is beyond anything I imagined.</font>

210
00:23:12.409 --> 00:23:15.037
<font color="#787878">~ Seven?
~ Seven....? A Horcrux.</font>

211
00:23:15.212 --> 00:23:16.645
<font color="#787878">They could be hidden anywhere.</font>

212
00:23:16.813 --> 00:23:19.008
<font color="#787878">To rip the soul into seven pieces....</font>

213
00:23:19.182 --> 00:23:22.151
<font color="#787878">~ If you did destroy each Horcrux....
~ One destroys Voldemort.</font>

214
00:23:25.756 --> 00:23:27.383
<font color="#787878">Trust me.</font>

215
00:23:28.325 --> 00:23:31.886
<font color="#787878">You lied to me. 
Lied to me, Ollivander.</font>

216
00:24:03.827 --> 00:24:05.761
<font color="#787878">Going somewhere?</font>

217
00:24:09.433 --> 00:24:13.529
<font color="#787878">Nobody else is going to die. Not for me.</font>

218
00:24:13.704 --> 00:24:15.501
<font color="#787878">For you?</font>

219
00:24:15.672 --> 00:24:17.902
<font color="#787878">You think Mad-Eye died for you?</font>

220
00:24:18.075 --> 00:24:21.010
<font color="#787878">You think George took that curse for you?</font>

221
00:24:21.778 --> 00:24:25.714
<font color="#787878">You may be the Chosen One, mate, but this is a whole lot bigger than that.</font>

222
00:24:25.882 --> 00:24:28.407
<font color="#787878">It's always been bigger than that.</font>

223
00:24:30.620 --> 00:24:33.111
<font color="#787878">~ Come with me.
~ What, and leave Hermione?</font>

224
00:24:33.590 --> 00:24:37.822
<font color="#787878">You mad?
We wouldn't last two days without her.</font>

225
00:24:39.229 --> 00:24:40.753
<font color="#787878">Don't tell her I said that.</font>

226
00:24:42.332 --> 00:24:45.529
<font color="#787878">Besides,
you've still got the Trace on you.</font>

227
00:24:45.702 --> 00:24:49.798
<font color="#787878">~ We've still got the wedding--
~ I don't care about a wedding.</font>

228
00:24:49.973 --> 00:24:54.842
<font color="#787878">I'm sorry. No matter whose it is. I have to start finding these Horcruxes.</font>

229
00:24:55.012 --> 00:24:56.980
<font color="#787878">They're our only chance to beat him....</font>

230
00:24:57.147 --> 00:25:00.116
<font color="#787878">....and the longer we stay here, the stronger he gets.</font>

231
00:25:01.551 --> 00:25:03.644
<font color="#787878">Tonight's not the night, mate.</font>

232
00:25:03.954 --> 00:25:06.422
<font color="#787878">We'd only be doing him a favor.</font>

233
00:25:34.184 --> 00:25:36.118
<font color="#787878">Do you think he knows?</font>

234
00:25:36.853 --> 00:25:42.723
<font color="#787878">I mean, they're bits of his soul, these Horcruxes. Bits of him.</font>

235
00:25:43.460 --> 00:25:47.726
<font color="#787878">When Dumbledore destroyed the ring, you destroyed Tom Riddle's diary....</font>

236
00:25:49.232 --> 00:25:51.826
<font color="#787878">....he must have felt something.</font>

237
00:25:52.602 --> 00:25:56.333
<font color="#787878">To kill the other Horcruxes, we have to find them.</font>

238
00:25:56.706 --> 00:25:58.674
<font color="#787878">Where are they?</font>

239
00:25:59.209 --> 00:26:01.268
<font color="#787878">Where do we start?</font>

240
00:26:04.714 --> 00:26:05.806
<font color="#787878">Ready when you are.</font>

241
00:26:07.551 --> 00:26:11.851
<font color="#787878">Please pay attention!
It's your brother's wedding. Buck up.</font>

242
00:26:37.280 --> 00:26:39.339
<font color="#787878">Zip me up, will you?</font>

243
00:26:53.196 --> 00:26:55.130
<font color="#787878">It seems silly, doesn't it, a wedding?</font>

244
00:26:55.632 --> 00:26:57.998
<font color="#787878">Given everything that's going on.</font>

245
00:26:59.336 --> 00:27:01.395
<font color="#787878">Maybe that's the best reason to have it....</font>

246
00:27:02.005 --> 00:27:04.530
<font color="#787878">....because of everything that's going on.</font>

247
00:27:20.590 --> 00:27:22.751
<font color="#787878">Morning.</font>

248
00:27:32.936 --> 00:27:35.097
<font color="#787878">Come on, keep up.</font>

249
00:27:35.772 --> 00:27:37.433
<font color="#787878">All together now.</font>

250
00:27:37.607 --> 00:27:43.045
<font color="#787878">One, two, three.</font>

251
00:27:53.123 --> 00:27:55.557
<font color="#787878">How's it looking at your end, boys?</font>

252
00:27:56.193 --> 00:27:58.127
<font color="#787878">Brilliant.</font>

253
00:28:00.230 --> 00:28:05.065
<font color="#787878">Bloody hell.
What's the Minister of Magic doing here?</font>

254
00:28:10.974 --> 00:28:12.839
<font color="#787878">To what do we owe the pleasure, Minister?</font>

255
00:28:13.009 --> 00:28:17.571
<font color="#787878">I think we both know the answer to that question, Mr. Potter.</font>

256
00:28:25.255 --> 00:28:27.155
<font color="#787878">And this is....?</font>

257
00:28:35.198 --> 00:28:39.100
<font color="#787878">"Herein is set forth
the last will and testament....</font>

258
00:28:39.269 --> 00:28:43.865
<font color="#787878">....of Albus Percival Wulfric Brian Dumbledore.</font>

259
00:28:44.040 --> 00:28:48.500
<font color="#787878">First, to Ronald Bilius Weasley....</font>

260
00:28:48.678 --> 00:28:51.977
<font color="#787878">....I leave my Deluminator....</font>

261
00:28:52.148 --> 00:28:54.412
<font color="#787878">....a device of my own making....</font>

262
00:28:54.584 --> 00:28:59.817
<font color="#787878">....in the hope that,
when things seem most dark....</font>

263
00:29:01.458 --> 00:29:04.325
<font color="#787878">....it will show him the light."</font>

264
00:29:10.233 --> 00:29:13.327
<font color="#787878">~ Dumbledore left this for me?
~ Yeah.</font>

265
00:29:14.271 --> 00:29:15.863
<font color="#787878">Brilliant.</font>

266
00:29:16.906 --> 00:29:18.737
<font color="#787878">What is it?</font>

267
00:29:30.887 --> 00:29:32.479
<font color="#787878">Wicked.</font>

268
00:29:34.791 --> 00:29:37.760
<font color="#787878">"To Hermione Jean Granger....</font>

269
00:29:37.927 --> 00:29:43.092
<font color="#787878">....I leave my copy of
The Tales of Beedle the Bard....</font>

270
00:29:43.266 --> 00:29:47.930
<font color="#787878">....in the hope that she find it entertaining and instructive."</font>

271
00:29:48.738 --> 00:29:50.069
<font color="#787878">Mom used to read me those.</font>

272
00:29:50.940 --> 00:29:52.464
<font color="#787878">"The Wizard and the Hopping Pot."</font>

273
00:29:52.642 --> 00:29:55.577
<font color="#787878">"Babbitty Rabbitty
and the Cackling Stump."</font>

274
00:29:57.347 --> 00:30:00.714
<font color="#787878">Come on, Babbitty Rabbitty.</font>

275
00:30:01.184 --> 00:30:02.879
<font color="#787878">No?</font>

276
00:30:03.219 --> 00:30:06.017
<font color="#787878">"To Harry James Potter....</font>

277
00:30:06.556 --> 00:30:10.287
<font color="#787878">....I leave the Snitch he caught in his first Quidditch match at Hogwarts....</font>

278
00:30:10.460 --> 00:30:15.488
<font color="#787878">....as a reminder
of the rewards of perseverance....</font>

279
00:30:17.734 --> 00:30:19.929
<font color="#787878">....and skill."</font>

280
00:30:39.989 --> 00:30:43.049
<font color="#787878">~ Is that it, then?
~ Not quite.</font>

281
00:30:43.226 --> 00:30:48.630
<font color="#787878">Dumbledore left you a second bequest:</font>

282
00:30:48.865 --> 00:30:51.857
<font color="#787878">The sword of Godric Gryffindor.</font>

283
00:30:53.470 --> 00:30:58.066
<font color="#787878">Unfortunately, the sword of Gryffindor was not Dumbledore's to give away.</font>

284
00:30:58.475 --> 00:31:01.205
<font color="#787878">As an important historical artifact, it belongs--</font>

285
00:31:01.378 --> 00:31:02.470
<font color="#787878">To Harry.</font>

286
00:31:03.313 --> 00:31:05.247
<font color="#787878">It belongs to Harry.</font>

287
00:31:05.415 --> 00:31:08.111
<font color="#787878">It came to him when he needed it in the Chamber of Secrets.</font>

288
00:31:08.284 --> 00:31:11.185
<font color="#787878">The sword may present itself to any worthy Gryffindor.</font>

289
00:31:11.354 --> 00:31:13.686
<font color="#787878">That does not make it
that wizard's property.</font>

290
00:31:15.125 --> 00:31:18.754
<font color="#787878">And, in any event, the current whereabouts of the sword are unknown.</font>

291
00:31:18.928 --> 00:31:21.522
<font color="#787878">~ Excuse me?
~ The sword is missing.</font>

292
00:31:22.899 --> 00:31:26.426
<font color="#787878">I don't know what you're up to, Mr. Potter....</font>

293
00:31:26.603 --> 00:31:30.562
<font color="#787878">....but you can't fight this war on your own.</font>

294
00:31:30.740 --> 00:31:33.140
<font color="#787878">He's too strong.</font>

295
00:32:34.337 --> 00:32:35.599
<font color="#787878">Hello, Harry.</font>

296
00:32:36.506 --> 00:32:40.499
<font color="#787878">I've interrupted a deep thought, haven't I? I can see it growing smaller in your eyes.</font>

297
00:32:40.677 --> 00:32:42.201
<font color="#787878">Of course not. How are you, Luna?</font>

298
00:32:42.378 --> 00:32:45.006
<font color="#787878">Very well. Got bitten by a garden gnome only moments ago.</font>

299
00:32:45.181 --> 00:32:47.513
<font color="#787878">Gnome saliva is very beneficial.</font>

300
00:32:47.684 --> 00:32:50.050
<font color="#787878">Xenophilius Lovegood.
We live just over the hill.</font>

301
00:32:50.220 --> 00:32:51.414
<font color="#787878">Pleasure to meet you, sir.</font>

302
00:32:51.588 --> 00:32:54.352
<font color="#787878">I trust you know, Mr. Potter, that we at The Quibbler....</font>

303
00:32:54.524 --> 00:32:56.856
<font color="#787878">....unlike those toadies
at The Daily Prophet....</font>

304
00:32:57.026 --> 00:32:59.620
<font color="#787878">....fully supported Dumbledore in his lifetime....</font>

305
00:32:59.796 --> 00:33:03.459
<font color="#787878">....and, in his death,
support you just as fully.</font>

306
00:33:03.766 --> 00:33:05.131
<font color="#787878">Thank you.</font>

307
00:33:05.301 --> 00:33:08.134
<font color="#787878">Come, Daddy.
Harry doesn't want to talk to us right now.</font>

308
00:33:08.304 --> 00:33:10.602
<font color="#787878">He's just too polite to say so.</font>

309
00:33:10.773 --> 00:33:12.832
<font color="#787878">Harry Potter.</font>

310
00:33:16.379 --> 00:33:18.506
<font color="#787878">Excuse me, sir? May I sit down?</font>

311
00:33:18.681 --> 00:33:22.082
<font color="#787878">Mr. Potter. By all means. Here.</font>

312
00:33:22.252 --> 00:33:23.913
<font color="#787878">Thanks.</font>

313
00:33:26.623 --> 00:33:29.922
<font color="#787878">I found what you wrote
in The Daily Prophet really moving.</font>

314
00:33:30.493 --> 00:33:33.291
<font color="#787878">You obviously knew Dumbledore well.</font>

315
00:33:33.463 --> 00:33:36.398
<font color="#787878">Well, I certainly knew him the longest.</font>

316
00:33:36.566 --> 00:33:39.296
<font color="#787878">That is, if you don't count his brother, Aberforth....</font>

317
00:33:39.469 --> 00:33:42.495
<font color="#787878">....and somehow, people never do seem to count Aberforth.</font>

318
00:33:42.839 --> 00:33:44.898
<font color="#787878">~ I didn't even know he had a brother.
~ Ah.</font>

319
00:33:45.074 --> 00:33:48.635
<font color="#787878">Well, Dumbledore was always very private, even as a boy.</font>

320
00:33:48.811 --> 00:33:50.210
<font color="#787878">Don't despair, Elphias.</font>

321
00:33:50.380 --> 00:33:54.817
<font color="#787878">I'm told he's been thoroughly unriddled by Rita Skeeter....</font>

322
00:33:54.984 --> 00:33:57.817
<font color="#787878">....in 800 pages, no less.</font>

323
00:33:58.454 --> 00:34:02.857
<font color="#787878">Word has it that someone talked to her.</font>

324
00:34:03.026 --> 00:34:05.824
<font color="#787878">Someone who knew
the Dumbledore family well.</font>

325
00:34:06.229 --> 00:34:09.824
<font color="#787878">Both you and I know who that is, Elphias.</font>

326
00:34:09.999 --> 00:34:11.466
<font color="#787878">A monstrous betrayal.</font>

327
00:34:13.369 --> 00:34:14.961
<font color="#787878">Who are we talking about?</font>

328
00:34:16.439 --> 00:34:18.566
<font color="#787878">Bathilda Bagshot.</font>

329
00:34:20.243 --> 00:34:21.301
<font color="#787878">~ Who?
~ My God, boy....</font>

330
00:34:21.477 --> 00:34:26.244
<font color="#787878">....she's only the most celebrated magical historian of the last century.</font>

331
00:34:27.951 --> 00:34:32.183
<font color="#787878">She was as close
to the Dumbledores as anyone.</font>

332
00:34:32.355 --> 00:34:37.383
<font color="#787878">Oh, I'm sure Rita Skeeter thought it well worth a trip to Godric's Hollow....</font>

333
00:34:37.560 --> 00:34:40.757
<font color="#787878">....to take a peek
into that old bird's rattled cage.</font>

334
00:34:40.930 --> 00:34:42.761
<font color="#787878">Godric's Hollow?</font>

335
00:34:43.199 --> 00:34:45.099
<font color="#787878">Bathilda Bagshot
lives at Godric's Hollow?</font>

336
00:34:45.501 --> 00:34:47.594
<font color="#787878">Well, that's where
she first met Dumbledore.</font>

337
00:34:47.770 --> 00:34:49.635
<font color="#787878">You don't mean to say
he lived there too?</font>

338
00:34:49.806 --> 00:34:53.367
<font color="#787878">The family moved there
after his father killed those three Muggles.</font>

339
00:34:53.543 --> 00:34:57.172
<font color="#787878">Oh, it was quite the scandal.</font>

340
00:34:57.347 --> 00:35:02.182
<font color="#787878">Honestly, my boy,
are you sure you knew him at all?</font>

341
00:35:28.645 --> 00:35:31.739
<font color="#787878">The Ministry has fallen.</font>

342
00:35:32.382 --> 00:35:36.284
<font color="#787878">The Minister of Magic is dead.</font>

343
00:35:38.755 --> 00:35:41.053
<font color="#787878">They are coming.</font>

344
00:35:41.224 --> 00:35:43.317
<font color="#787878">They are coming.</font>

345
00:35:44.594 --> 00:35:46.084
<font color="#787878">They are coming.</font>

346
00:35:46.262 --> 00:35:47.729
<font color="#787878">They're coming!</font>

347
00:35:49.766 --> 00:35:51.597
<font color="#787878">Nice meeting you, Mr. Potter.</font>

348
00:36:02.679 --> 00:36:05.045
<font color="#787878">~ Ginny!
~ Harry! Go!</font>

349
00:36:05.214 --> 00:36:06.272
<font color="#787878">Go!</font>

350
00:36:19.595 --> 00:36:22.189
<font color="#787878">Here you go, sightseeing tour? Leaves in 15 minutes.</font>

351
00:36:23.633 --> 00:36:26.261
<font color="#787878">~ Where are we?
~ Shaftesbury Avenue.</font>

352
00:36:26.436 --> 00:36:29.633
<font color="#787878">I used to come to the theater here with Mom and Dad.</font>

353
00:36:29.939 --> 00:36:33.033
<font color="#787878">I don't know why I thought of it. It just popped into my head.</font>

354
00:36:33.443 --> 00:36:35.274
<font color="#787878">This way.</font>

355
00:36:39.082 --> 00:36:41.175
<font color="#787878">We need to change.</font>

356
00:36:47.123 --> 00:36:48.385
<font color="#787878">How the ruddy....?</font>

357
00:36:48.558 --> 00:36:51.118
<font color="#787878">Undetectable Extension Charm.</font>

358
00:36:51.561 --> 00:36:53.825
<font color="#787878">You're amazing, you are.</font>

359
00:36:54.030 --> 00:36:56.590
<font color="#787878">Always the tone of surprise.</font>

360
00:36:58.601 --> 00:37:00.728
<font color="#787878">Ah. That'll be the books.</font>

361
00:37:06.242 --> 00:37:08.107
<font color="#787878">What about all the people
at the wedding?</font>

362
00:37:08.277 --> 00:37:10.745
<font color="#787878">~ Do you think we should go back?
~ They were after you.</font>

363
00:37:10.913 --> 00:37:13.074
<font color="#787878">We'd put everyone in danger by going back.</font>

364
00:37:14.951 --> 00:37:16.680
<font color="#787878">~ Ron's right.
~ Ahem.</font>

365
00:37:16.853 --> 00:37:18.514
<font color="#787878">Coffee?</font>

366
00:37:19.055 --> 00:37:22.081
<font color="#787878">~ A cappuccino, please.
~ You?</font>

367
00:37:22.925 --> 00:37:26.224
<font color="#787878">~ What she said.
~ Same.</font>

368
00:37:29.599 --> 00:37:33.433
<font color="#787878">So where do we go from here? Leaky Cauldron?</font>

369
00:37:33.803 --> 00:37:34.895
<font color="#787878">It's too dangerous.</font>

370
00:37:35.805 --> 00:37:39.332
<font color="#787878">If Voldemort has taken over the Ministry, none of the old places are safe.</font>

371
00:37:39.509 --> 00:37:42.569
<font color="#787878">Everyone from the wedding
will have gone underground, into hiding.</font>

372
00:37:42.745 --> 00:37:45.236
<font color="#787878">My rucksack with all my things, I've left it at the Burrow.</font>

373
00:37:50.386 --> 00:37:52.286
<font color="#787878">You're joking.</font>

374
00:37:53.890 --> 00:37:57.849
<font color="#787878">I've had all the essentials packed for days, just in case.</font>

375
00:37:58.027 --> 00:38:00.222
<font color="#787878">By the way, these jeans, not my favorite.</font>

376
00:38:01.397 --> 00:38:02.455
<font color="#787878">Down!</font>

377
00:38:03.599 --> 00:38:04.896
<font color="#787878">Stupefy!</font>

378
00:38:09.105 --> 00:38:10.834
<font color="#787878">Expulso!</font>

379
00:38:20.750 --> 00:38:22.581
<font color="#787878">Petrificus Totalus.</font>

380
00:38:26.722 --> 00:38:27.780
<font color="#787878">Go.</font>

381
00:38:28.224 --> 00:38:29.384
<font color="#787878">Leave.</font>

382
00:38:34.063 --> 00:38:36.861
<font color="#787878">Lock the door, get the lights.</font>

383
00:38:46.108 --> 00:38:47.837
<font color="#787878">This one's name is Rowle.</font>

384
00:38:48.344 --> 00:38:51.780
<font color="#787878">He was on the Astronomy Tower the night Snape killed Dumbledore.</font>

385
00:38:52.582 --> 00:38:57.076
<font color="#787878">This is Dolohov. I recognize him from the wanted posters.</font>

386
00:38:58.154 --> 00:39:00.315
<font color="#787878">So, what we gonna do with you, hey?</font>

387
00:39:01.190 --> 00:39:03.283
<font color="#787878">Kill us if it was turned round, wouldn't you?</font>

388
00:39:03.459 --> 00:39:04.790
<font color="#787878">If we kill them, they'll know we were here.</font>

389
00:39:04.961 --> 00:39:06.360
<font color="#787878">Ron.</font>

390
00:39:06.529 --> 00:39:10.488
<font color="#787878">Suppose he did Mad-Eye.
How would you feel then?</font>

391
00:39:12.468 --> 00:39:14.095
<font color="#787878">It's better we wipe their memories.</font>

392
00:39:14.971 --> 00:39:16.939
<font color="#787878">You're the boss.</font>

393
00:39:17.240 --> 00:39:19.003
<font color="#787878">Hermione....</font>

394
00:39:21.477 --> 00:39:23.945
<font color="#787878">....you're the best at spells.</font>

395
00:39:41.597 --> 00:39:43.792
<font color="#787878">Obliviate.</font>

396
00:39:56.145 --> 00:39:57.737
<font color="#787878">How is it they knew we were there?</font>

397
00:39:57.914 --> 00:39:59.506
<font color="#787878">Maybe you still have the Trace on you?</font>

398
00:39:59.682 --> 00:40:03.118
<font color="#787878">Can't be. Trace breaks at 17. It's wizarding law.</font>

399
00:40:04.921 --> 00:40:06.479
<font color="#787878">What?</font>

400
00:40:07.290 --> 00:40:10.259
<font color="#787878">We didn't celebrate your birthday, Harry.</font>

401
00:40:10.626 --> 00:40:13.891
<font color="#787878">Ginny and I, we prepared a cake.</font>

402
00:40:14.063 --> 00:40:17.032
<font color="#787878">We were going to bring it out at the end of the wedding.</font>

403
00:40:17.199 --> 00:40:20.635
<font color="#787878">I appreciate the thought, but given the fact that we were almost killed....</font>

404
00:40:20.803 --> 00:40:23.203
<font color="#787878">....by a couple of Death Eaters a few minutes ago....</font>

405
00:40:24.874 --> 00:40:26.569
<font color="#787878">Right.</font>

406
00:40:27.376 --> 00:40:28.400
<font color="#787878">Perspective.</font>

407
00:40:28.577 --> 00:40:31.569
<font color="#787878">We need to get off the streets, get somewhere safe.</font>

408
00:41:04.680 --> 00:41:06.705
<font color="#787878">What was that all about?</font>

409
00:41:07.683 --> 00:41:13.519
<font color="#787878">Probably Mad-Eye's idea,
in case Snape decided to come snooping.</font>

410
00:41:21.697 --> 00:41:23.665
<font color="#787878">Homenum Revelio.</font>

411
00:41:30.306 --> 00:41:32.137
<font color="#787878">We're alone.</font>

412
00:41:38.948 --> 00:41:41.178
<font color="#787878">I believed another wand-</font>

413
00:41:41.350 --> 00:41:43.818
<font color="#787878">You lied to me.
It makes no sense.</font>

414
00:41:46.655 --> 00:41:49.624
<font color="#787878">I believed a different wand would work, I swear.</font>

415
00:41:51.127 --> 00:41:53.186
<font color="#787878">There must be another way.</font>

416
00:43:03.532 --> 00:43:07.263
<font color="#787878">Harry? Hermione, where are you?</font>

417
00:43:07.536 --> 00:43:09.868
<font color="#787878">I think I've found something.</font>

418
00:43:16.178 --> 00:43:17.236
<font color="#787878">Lovely.</font>

419
00:43:22.918 --> 00:43:26.410
<font color="#787878">"Regulus Arcturus Black."</font>

420
00:43:26.589 --> 00:43:28.284
<font color="#787878">R.A.B.</font>

421
00:43:31.894 --> 00:43:35.193
<font color="#787878">"I know I will be dead
long before you read this.</font>

422
00:43:35.364 --> 00:43:39.391
<font color="#787878">I have stolen the real Horcrux and intend to destroy it."</font>

423
00:43:39.768 --> 00:43:42.168
<font color="#787878">R.A.B. is Sirius's brother.</font>

424
00:43:42.605 --> 00:43:44.368
<font color="#787878">Yes.</font>

425
00:43:46.475 --> 00:43:50.343
<font color="#787878">Question is,
did he actually destroy the real Horcrux?</font>

426
00:44:12.067 --> 00:44:14.228
<font color="#787878">You've been spying on us, have you?</font>

427
00:44:14.403 --> 00:44:18.863
<font color="#787878">Kreacher has been watching.</font>

428
00:44:19.041 --> 00:44:20.975
<font color="#787878">Maybe he knows where the real locket is.</font>

429
00:44:23.979 --> 00:44:25.913
<font color="#787878">Have you ever seen this before?</font>

430
00:44:26.081 --> 00:44:27.673
<font color="#787878">Kreacher?</font>

431
00:44:28.517 --> 00:44:30.951
<font color="#787878">It's Master Regulus' locket.</font>

432
00:44:31.120 --> 00:44:33.816
<font color="#787878">But there were two, weren't there?</font>

433
00:44:34.823 --> 00:44:36.518
<font color="#787878">Where's the other one?</font>

434
00:44:39.028 --> 00:44:43.590
<font color="#787878">Kreacher doesn't know
where the other locket is.</font>

435
00:44:43.766 --> 00:44:46.166
<font color="#787878">Yes, but did you ever see it? Was it in this house?</font>

436
00:44:46.335 --> 00:44:47.495
<font color="#787878">Filthy Mudblood.</font>

437
00:44:47.670 --> 00:44:49.365
<font color="#787878">~ Death Eaters are coming--
~ Ron.</font>

438
00:44:49.538 --> 00:44:52.371
<font color="#787878">~ Blood traitor, Weasley.
~ Answer her.</font>

439
00:44:54.143 --> 00:44:56.373
<font color="#787878">Yes.</font>

440
00:44:57.413 --> 00:45:00.871
<font color="#787878">It was here in this house.</font>

441
00:45:02.151 --> 00:45:04.483
<font color="#787878">A most evil object.</font>

442
00:45:04.653 --> 00:45:05.881
<font color="#787878">How do you mean?</font>

443
00:45:06.655 --> 00:45:10.955
<font color="#787878">Before Master Regulus died, he ordered Kreacher to destroy it....</font>

444
00:45:11.126 --> 00:45:16.393
<font color="#787878">....but no matter how hard Kreacher tried, he could not do it.</font>

445
00:45:16.565 --> 00:45:18.157
<font color="#787878">Well, where is it now?</font>

446
00:45:18.801 --> 00:45:23.397
<font color="#787878">~ Did someone take it?
~ He came in the night.</font>

447
00:45:23.572 --> 00:45:28.236
<font color="#787878">He took many things,
including the locket.</font>

448
00:45:28.410 --> 00:45:29.934
<font color="#787878">Who did?</font>

449
00:45:30.613 --> 00:45:32.205
<font color="#787878">Who was it, Kreacher?</font>

450
00:45:34.750 --> 00:45:37.412
<font color="#787878">Mundungus.</font>

451
00:45:37.586 --> 00:45:41.078
<font color="#787878">Mundungus Fletcher.</font>

452
00:45:42.157 --> 00:45:43.749
<font color="#787878">Find him.</font>

453
00:46:05.281 --> 00:46:06.748
<font color="#787878">My father will hear about this.</font>

454
00:46:12.054 --> 00:46:13.919
<font color="#787878">Hey, losers.</font>

455
00:46:14.657 --> 00:46:16.921
<font color="#787878">He isn't here.</font>

456
00:46:30.539 --> 00:46:32.939
<font color="#787878">As your new Minister for Magic....</font>

457
00:46:33.142 --> 00:46:38.307
<font color="#787878">....I promise to restore
this temple of tolerance....</font>

458
00:46:38.480 --> 00:46:40.141
<font color="#787878">....to its former glory.</font>

459
00:46:41.550 --> 00:46:43.381
<font color="#787878">Therefore, beginning today....</font>

460
00:46:44.453 --> 00:46:48.219
<font color="#787878">....each employee
will submit themselves....</font>

461
00:46:48.891 --> 00:46:51.121
<font color="#787878">....for evaluation.</font>

462
00:46:51.994 --> 00:46:54.986
<font color="#787878">You have nothing to fear....</font>

463
00:46:56.432 --> 00:46:58.161
<font color="#787878">....if you have nothing to hide.</font>

464
00:47:02.571 --> 00:47:04.163
<font color="#787878">~ How much?
~ Two Galleons.</font>

465
00:47:04.340 --> 00:47:06.831
<font color="#787878">Come on, time is money. Cheers, pal.</font>

466
00:47:07.009 --> 00:47:08.943
<font color="#787878">~ Snatchers!
~ Move out of the way.</font>

467
00:47:15.150 --> 00:47:16.617
<font color="#787878">~ I told you.
~ Get out.</font>

468
00:47:16.785 --> 00:47:17.809
<font color="#787878">Squash him.</font>

469
00:47:27.029 --> 00:47:28.656
<font color="#787878">Be a bit gentler.</font>

470
00:47:54.757 --> 00:47:56.884
<font color="#787878">They have flesh memories.</font>

471
00:47:59.027 --> 00:48:04.556
<font color="#787878">When Scrimgeour first gave it to you, I thought it might open at your touch.</font>

472
00:48:05.401 --> 00:48:08.165
<font color="#787878">That Dumbledore had hidden
something inside it.</font>

473
00:48:08.404 --> 00:48:10.065
<font color="#787878">Many of you are wondering....</font>

474
00:48:10.239 --> 00:48:13.174
<font color="#787878">....why Voldemort has yet to show himself now that he has vanquished....</font>

475
00:48:13.342 --> 00:48:16.402
<font color="#787878">....the most powerful symbol of opposition to him and his followers.</font>

476
00:48:18.447 --> 00:48:19.471
<font color="#787878">Get off.</font>

477
00:48:19.648 --> 00:48:22.412
<font color="#787878">Harry Potter, so long it's been.</font>

478
00:48:22.885 --> 00:48:24.216
<font color="#787878">Get off me.</font>

479
00:48:29.825 --> 00:48:33.761
<font color="#787878">As requested,
Kreacher has returned with the thief....</font>

480
00:48:33.929 --> 00:48:35.920
<font color="#787878">~ Expellliarmus.
~ .... Mundungus Fletcher.</font>

481
00:48:36.098 --> 00:48:39.295
<font color="#787878">What you playing at? Setting a pair of bleeding house-elves after me.</font>

482
00:48:39.468 --> 00:48:40.958
<font color="#787878">Dobby was only trying to help.</font>

483
00:48:41.136 --> 00:48:45.505
<font color="#787878">Dobby saw Kreacher in Diagon Alley,
which Dobby thought was curious.</font>

484
00:48:45.674 --> 00:48:50.008
<font color="#787878">And then Dobby heard Kreacher mention Harry Potter's name.</font>

485
00:48:50.179 --> 00:48:53.012
<font color="#787878">~ I just--
~ And then Dobby saw Kreacher....</font>

486
00:48:53.182 --> 00:48:55.980
<font color="#787878">~ ....talking with the thief, Mundungus--
~ I'm no thief.</font>

487
00:48:56.151 --> 00:48:59.086
<font color="#787878">You foul little-- Git.</font>

488
00:48:59.488 --> 00:49:03.891
<font color="#787878">I'm a purveyor
of rare and wondrous objects.</font>

489
00:49:04.059 --> 00:49:05.924
<font color="#787878">You're a thief, Dung. Everyone knows it.</font>

490
00:49:06.094 --> 00:49:09.063
<font color="#787878">Master Weasley,
so good to see you again.</font>

491
00:49:09.231 --> 00:49:10.255
<font color="#787878">Wicked trainers.</font>

492
00:49:12.000 --> 00:49:14.764
<font color="#787878">Listen, I panicked that night, all right?</font>

493
00:49:16.405 --> 00:49:18.635
<font color="#787878">Could I help it
if Mad-Eye fell off his broom?</font>

494
00:49:20.642 --> 00:49:22.075
<font color="#787878">~ You....
~ Tell the truth.</font>

495
00:49:22.244 --> 00:49:25.008
<font color="#787878">When you turned this place over-- Don't deny it.</font>

496
00:49:25.180 --> 00:49:26.704
<font color="#787878">--you found a locket, am I right?</font>

497
00:49:26.882 --> 00:49:29.146
<font color="#787878">Why? Was it valuable?</font>

498
00:49:29.318 --> 00:49:30.444
<font color="#787878">You still got it?</font>

499
00:49:30.619 --> 00:49:33.053
<font color="#787878">No, he's worried
he didn't get enough money for it.</font>

500
00:49:33.222 --> 00:49:34.746
<font color="#787878">Bleeding give it away, didn't I?</font>

501
00:49:36.124 --> 00:49:39.252
<font color="#787878">There I was,
flogging me wares in Diagon Alley....</font>

502
00:49:39.428 --> 00:49:43.387
<font color="#787878">....when some Ministry hag comes up and asks to see me license.</font>

503
00:49:43.632 --> 00:49:45.691
<font color="#787878">Says she's a mind to lock me up.</font>

504
00:49:45.868 --> 00:49:49.531
<font color="#787878">And would've done it too,
if she hadn't taken a fancy to that locket.</font>

505
00:49:49.705 --> 00:49:53.641
<font color="#787878">~ Who was she? The witch. Do you know?
~ No, I--</font>

506
00:49:58.447 --> 00:50:01.848
<font color="#787878">Well, she's there. Look.</font>

507
00:50:03.986 --> 00:50:06.352
<font color="#787878">Bleeding bow and all.</font>

508
00:50:47.195 --> 00:50:50.961
<font color="#787878">Right, remember what we said.</font>

509
00:50:51.233 --> 00:50:54.964
<font color="#787878">Don't speak to anyone
unless absolutely necessary.</font>

510
00:50:55.237 --> 00:51:00.140
<font color="#787878">Just try and act normal.
Do what everybody else is doing.</font>

511
00:51:00.576 --> 00:51:03.704
<font color="#787878">If we do that, then with a bit of luck, we'll get inside.</font>

512
00:51:03.879 --> 00:51:05.471
<font color="#787878">~ And then--
~ It gets really tricky.</font>

513
00:51:05.647 --> 00:51:07.512
<font color="#787878">~ Correct.
~ Yeah.</font>

514
00:51:07.683 --> 00:51:10.584
<font color="#787878">~ This is completely mental.
~ Completely.</font>

515
00:51:10.752 --> 00:51:12.777
<font color="#787878">The world's mental.</font>

516
00:51:12.955 --> 00:51:14.388
<font color="#787878">Come on....</font>

517
00:51:14.990 --> 00:51:17.424
<font color="#787878">....we've got a Horcrux to find.</font>

518
00:52:11.313 --> 00:52:13.713
<font color="#787878">We flush ourselves in.</font>

519
00:52:17.753 --> 00:52:20.517
<font color="#787878">That's bloody disgusting.</font>

520
00:52:48.550 --> 00:52:50.211
<font color="#787878">Name?</font>

521
00:52:51.520 --> 00:52:53.044
<font color="#787878">You. Come.</font>

522
00:52:53.221 --> 00:52:55.382
<font color="#787878">~ What? What?
~ Come on.</font>

523
00:52:55.557 --> 00:52:57.991
<font color="#787878">~ What did I do?
~ Just keep walking.</font>

524
00:53:05.367 --> 00:53:07.301
<font color="#787878">~ Are those--?
~ Muggles.</font>

525
00:53:07.469 --> 00:53:12.065
<font color="#787878">In their rightful place.</font>

526
00:53:13.842 --> 00:53:17.039
<font color="#787878">Gotta tell you,
I'm starting to freak out a bit.</font>

527
00:53:19.314 --> 00:53:23.808
<font color="#787878">How long did you say this batch of Polyjuice would last, Hermione?</font>

528
00:53:24.352 --> 00:53:25.376
<font color="#787878">I didn't.</font>

529
00:53:32.561 --> 00:53:34.495
<font color="#787878">Cattermole.</font>

530
00:53:35.530 --> 00:53:39.125
<font color="#787878">It's still raining inside my office. That's two days now.</font>

531
00:53:41.069 --> 00:53:42.832
<font color="#787878">Have you tried an umbrella?</font>

532
00:53:43.805 --> 00:53:46.740
<font color="#787878">You do realize I'm going downstairs, don't you, Cattermole?</font>

533
00:53:47.309 --> 00:53:51.268
<font color="#787878">~ Downstairs?
~ To interrogate your wife.</font>

534
00:53:52.180 --> 00:53:56.116
<font color="#787878">Now, if my wife's blood status were in doubt....</font>

535
00:53:56.284 --> 00:53:59.185
<font color="#787878">....and the head of the Department of Magical Law Enforcement....</font>

536
00:53:59.354 --> 00:54:04.917
<font color="#787878">....needed a job doing,
I think I might just make that a priority.</font>

537
00:54:05.494 --> 00:54:07.689
<font color="#787878">You have one hour.</font>

538
00:54:19.441 --> 00:54:25.107
<font color="#787878">Oh, my God. What am I gonna do? My wife's all alone downstairs.</font>

539
00:54:25.413 --> 00:54:29.679
<font color="#787878">~ Ron, you don't have a wife.
~ Oh, right.</font>

540
00:54:29.851 --> 00:54:31.819
<font color="#787878">Level 2.</font>

541
00:54:32.621 --> 00:54:34.748
<font color="#787878">But how do I stop it raining?</font>

542
00:54:34.923 --> 00:54:37.517
<font color="#787878">Try "Finite Incantatem."</font>

543
00:54:37.692 --> 00:54:39.557
<font color="#787878">Department of Magical Law Enforcement....</font>

544
00:54:39.728 --> 00:54:41.161
<font color="#787878">....and Improper Use of Magic Department.</font>

545
00:54:41.329 --> 00:54:43.297
<font color="#787878">This is you, Ron.</font>

546
00:54:47.536 --> 00:54:52.371
<font color="#787878">Finite Incantatem. Okay.
And if that doesn't work....?</font>

547
00:55:04.286 --> 00:55:07.221
<font color="#787878">Level 1,
Minister of Magic and support staff.</font>

548
00:55:07.389 --> 00:55:09.516
<font color="#787878">If we don't locate Umbridge within the hour....</font>

549
00:55:09.691 --> 00:55:11.682
<font color="#787878">....we go find Ron
and come back another day.</font>

550
00:55:11.860 --> 00:55:12.884
<font color="#787878">~ Deal?
~ Yes.</font>

551
00:55:16.464 --> 00:55:18.796
<font color="#787878">Ah, Mafalda. Travers sent you, did he?</font>

552
00:55:18.967 --> 00:55:22.027
<font color="#787878">Good, we'll go straight down.</font>

553
00:55:24.372 --> 00:55:26.897
<font color="#787878">Albert, aren't you getting out?</font>

554
00:56:00.275 --> 00:56:02.300
<font color="#787878">Runcorn.</font>

555
00:56:54.796 --> 00:56:56.195
<font color="#787878">Accio locket.</font>

556
00:57:50.885 --> 00:57:54.048
<font color="#787878">All right, all right.
Let's calm down, shall we?</font>

557
00:57:54.956 --> 00:57:57.424
<font color="#787878">Let's get back to work, please.</font>

558
00:57:58.226 --> 00:58:00.057
<font color="#787878">Calm down.</font>

559
00:58:05.400 --> 00:58:07.095
<font color="#787878">Runcorn.</font>

560
00:58:14.909 --> 00:58:16.672
<font color="#787878">Morning.</font>

561
00:58:18.380 --> 00:58:20.814
<font color="#787878">Ron, it's me.</font>

562
00:58:20.982 --> 00:58:24.816
<font color="#787878">Harry.
Blimey, forgot what you looked like.</font>

563
00:58:24.986 --> 00:58:26.419
<font color="#787878">Where's Hermione?</font>

564
00:58:26.588 --> 00:58:30.024
<font color="#787878">She's gone down to the courtrooms, with Umbridge.</font>

565
00:58:36.865 --> 00:58:38.992
<font color="#787878">Bloody cold down here.</font>

566
00:58:39.167 --> 00:58:42.762
<font color="#787878">I'm a half-blood. My father was a wizard.</font>

567
00:58:42.937 --> 00:58:45.269
<font color="#787878">William Alderton.
He worked here for 30 years.</font>

568
00:58:45.440 --> 00:58:48.876
<font color="#787878">Perhaps you know him.
Always wore his jacket inside out.</font>

569
00:58:49.044 --> 00:58:51.512
<font color="#787878">No, there's been a mistake. I'm half-blood, you see.</font>

570
00:58:51.679 --> 00:58:54.876
<font color="#787878">We must go back. I'm half-blood.</font>

571
00:59:04.993 --> 00:59:07.086
<font color="#787878">~ Mary Elizabeth Cattermole?
~ Yes.</font>

572
00:59:07.262 --> 00:59:12.199
<font color="#787878">Of 27 Chislehurst Gardens,
Great Tolling, Evesham?</font>

573
00:59:12.367 --> 00:59:13.391
<font color="#787878">~ Yes.
~ It's here.</font>

574
00:59:13.568 --> 00:59:18.369
<font color="#787878">Mother to Maisie, Ellie and Alfred? Wife to Reginald?</font>

575
00:59:22.577 --> 00:59:23.635
<font color="#787878">Reg?</font>

576
00:59:35.223 --> 00:59:37.054
<font color="#787878">Thank you, Albert.</font>

577
00:59:39.661 --> 00:59:42.391
<font color="#787878">Mary Elizabeth Cattermole?</font>

578
00:59:44.599 --> 00:59:45.657
<font color="#787878">Yes.</font>

579
00:59:46.701 --> 00:59:50.228
<font color="#787878">A wand was taken from you
upon your arrival at the Ministry today.</font>

580
00:59:50.405 --> 00:59:53.169
<font color="#787878">Is this that wand?</font>

581
00:59:55.009 --> 00:59:59.537
<font color="#787878">Would you please tell the court from which witch or wizard you took this wand?</font>

582
00:59:59.714 --> 01:00:02.148
<font color="#787878">I didn't take it.</font>

583
01:00:03.384 --> 01:00:09.186
<font color="#787878">I got it in Diagon Alley, at Ollivander's, when I was 11.</font>

584
01:00:10.625 --> 01:00:13.116
<font color="#787878">It chose me.</font>

585
01:00:14.496 --> 01:00:16.259
<font color="#787878">You're lying.</font>

586
01:00:16.698 --> 01:00:21.260
<font color="#787878">Wands only choose witches,
and you are not a witch.</font>

587
01:00:21.436 --> 01:00:23.461
<font color="#787878">But I am.</font>

588
01:00:23.905 --> 01:00:26.965
<font color="#787878">Tell them, Reg. Tell them what I am.</font>

589
01:00:29.511 --> 01:00:30.876
<font color="#787878">Reg, tell them what I am.</font>

590
01:00:40.855 --> 01:00:42.618
<font color="#787878">What on earth are you doing, Albert?</font>

591
01:00:45.527 --> 01:00:47.427
<font color="#787878">You're lying, Dolores.</font>

592
01:00:49.797 --> 01:00:52.357
<font color="#787878">And one mustn't tell lies.</font>

593
01:00:53.168 --> 01:00:54.465
<font color="#787878">Stupefy!</font>

594
01:01:02.177 --> 01:01:03.542
<font color="#787878">It's Harry Potter.</font>

595
01:01:03.711 --> 01:01:06.179
<font color="#787878">It is, isn't it?
This'll be one to tell the kids.</font>

596
01:01:22.197 --> 01:01:23.357
<font color="#787878">Expecto Patronum!</font>

597
01:01:47.222 --> 01:01:49.656
<font color="#787878">Oh. Oh. Oh.</font>

598
01:01:49.824 --> 01:01:51.849
<font color="#787878">Mary, go home.</font>

599
01:01:53.294 --> 01:01:54.761
<font color="#787878">Get the kids.</font>

600
01:01:54.929 --> 01:01:58.296
<font color="#787878">I'll meet you there. We have to get out of the country, understand?</font>

601
01:01:58.466 --> 01:02:00.934
<font color="#787878">Mary, do as I say.</font>

602
01:02:15.350 --> 01:02:16.510
<font color="#787878">Mary?</font>

603
01:02:18.152 --> 01:02:20.052
<font color="#787878">Who's that?</font>

604
01:02:21.189 --> 01:02:24.181
<font color="#787878">Long story. Nice meeting you.</font>

605
01:02:24.359 --> 01:02:25.724
<font color="#787878">It's Harry Potter.</font>

606
01:02:26.427 --> 01:02:28.395
<font color="#787878">It's Harry. Harry Potter.</font>

607
01:02:28.563 --> 01:02:30.588
<font color="#787878">~ There he is.
~ Get him!</font>

608
01:02:30.765 --> 01:02:32.858
<font color="#787878">~ Get him!
~ Stop him!</font>

609
01:02:44.779 --> 01:02:45.939
<font color="#787878">~ Watch out.
~ Look out.</font>

610
01:02:46.314 --> 01:02:47.713
<font color="#787878">This way!</font>

611
01:03:06.701 --> 01:03:08.532
<font color="#787878">Expellliarmus!</font>

612
01:03:55.983 --> 01:03:57.041
<font color="#787878">Oh, my God.</font>

613
01:03:57.218 --> 01:04:00.847
<font color="#787878">Shh, shh, shh. It's all right. It's okay.</font>

614
01:04:03.257 --> 01:04:06.522
<font color="#787878">Harry. Harry, quickly, in my bag.</font>

615
01:04:06.694 --> 01:04:09.219
<font color="#787878">There's a bottle labeled
"Essence of Dittany."</font>

616
01:04:11.799 --> 01:04:14.597
<font color="#787878">Shh. Shh.</font>

617
01:04:14.769 --> 01:04:17.465
<font color="#787878">Okay, okay. Quickly.</font>

618
01:04:18.239 --> 01:04:20.332
<font color="#787878">~ Accio Dittany.
Shh.</font>

619
01:04:20.708 --> 01:04:23.438
<font color="#787878">It's all right. Unstopper it.</font>

620
01:04:23.611 --> 01:04:25.101
<font color="#787878">Hermione, his arm.</font>

621
01:04:25.279 --> 01:04:27.270
<font color="#787878">I know, just do it.</font>

622
01:04:28.015 --> 01:04:29.744
<font color="#787878">It's okay.</font>

623
01:04:31.018 --> 01:04:34.977
<font color="#787878">~ Okay, it's gonna sting a little bit.
~ What happened? I thought we meant....</font>

624
01:04:35.156 --> 01:04:37.886
<font color="#787878">~ ....to be going back to Grimmauld Place.
~ We were. We were. Shh.</font>

625
01:04:38.059 --> 01:04:39.890
<font color="#787878">It's all right. One more, one more.</font>

626
01:04:40.061 --> 01:04:44.589
<font color="#787878">We were there, we were there, but Yaxley had hold of me, and I....</font>

627
01:04:44.766 --> 01:04:47.792
<font color="#787878">I knew once he'd seen where we were, we couldn't stay....</font>

628
01:04:47.969 --> 01:04:51.097
<font color="#787878">....so I brought us here....</font>

629
01:04:51.572 --> 01:04:54.200
<font color="#787878">....but Ron got splinched.</font>

630
01:04:57.278 --> 01:04:59.075
<font color="#787878">It's all right.</font>

631
01:05:18.132 --> 01:05:20.498
<font color="#787878">Protego Totalum.</font>

632
01:05:21.969 --> 01:05:23.436
<font color="#787878">Salvio Hexia.</font>

633
01:05:23.604 --> 01:05:25.003
<font color="#787878">What are you doing?</font>

634
01:05:25.173 --> 01:05:27.471
<font color="#787878">Protective enchantments.</font>

635
01:05:27.642 --> 01:05:31.237
<font color="#787878">I don't fancy another visit like the one we had in Shaftesbury Avenue, do you?</font>

636
01:05:31.412 --> 01:05:33.107
<font color="#787878">You can get going on the tent.</font>

637
01:05:33.781 --> 01:05:35.612
<font color="#787878">~ Tent?
Protego Totalum.</font>

638
01:05:35.783 --> 01:05:37.910
<font color="#787878">Where am I supposed to find a tent?</font>

639
01:05:38.085 --> 01:05:42.385
<font color="#787878">Repello Muggletum. Muffliato.</font>

640
01:05:52.700 --> 01:05:54.600
<font color="#787878">You first.</font>

641
01:05:57.605 --> 01:05:59.698
<font color="#787878">Dissendium.</font>

642
01:06:13.321 --> 01:06:15.221
<font color="#787878">Incendio.</font>

643
01:06:20.628 --> 01:06:22.653
<font color="#787878">Expulso.</font>

644
01:06:29.871 --> 01:06:31.998
<font color="#787878">Diffindo.</font>

645
01:06:33.441 --> 01:06:34.465
<font color="#787878">Reducto.</font>

646
01:06:55.897 --> 01:06:57.762
<font color="#787878">What are you doing?</font>

647
01:06:59.166 --> 01:07:01.930
<font color="#787878">We have to keep it safe
until we find out how to destroy it.</font>

648
01:07:02.103 --> 01:07:04.799
<font color="#787878">Seems strange, mate.
Dumbledore sends you off....</font>

649
01:07:04.972 --> 01:07:08.738
<font color="#787878">....to find all these Horcruxes, but doesn't tell you how to destroy them.</font>

650
01:07:08.910 --> 01:07:10.537
<font color="#787878">Doesn't that bother you?</font>

651
01:07:22.924 --> 01:07:26.325
<font color="#787878">A goblin by 
the name of Gornuk was killed.</font>

652
01:07:26.494 --> 01:07:29.554
<font color="#787878">It is believed that Muggle-born Dean Thomas and a second goblin....</font>

653
01:07:29.730 --> 01:07:32.665
<font color="#787878">....both believed to have been traveling with Tonks, Cresswell....</font>

654
01:07:32.833 --> 01:07:34.357
<font color="#787878">....and Gornuk, may have escaped.</font>

655
01:07:34.535 --> 01:07:38.301
<font color="#787878">If Dean is listening or anyone has any knowledge of his whereabouts....</font>

656
01:07:38.472 --> 01:07:41.532
<font color="#787878">....his parents and sisters are desperate for news.</font>

657
01:07:41.709 --> 01:07:45.076
<font color="#787878">Meanwhile, a Muggle family of five has been found dead in their home.</font>

658
01:07:45.246 --> 01:07:48.511
<font color="#787878">You know the spell, Harry.</font>

659
01:07:52.253 --> 01:07:53.515
<font color="#787878">Tell me.</font>

660
01:07:56.157 --> 01:07:57.988
<font color="#787878">Tell me, Gregorovitch.</font>

661
01:07:58.159 --> 01:07:59.786
<font color="#787878">It was stolen from me.</font>

662
01:07:59.961 --> 01:08:03.419
<font color="#787878">Who was he? The thief?</font>

663
01:08:06.567 --> 01:08:10.526
<font color="#787878">It was a boy. 
It was he who took it.</font>

664
01:08:10.905 --> 01:08:13.203
<font color="#787878">I never saw it again.</font>

665
01:08:13.374 --> 01:08:15.171
<font color="#787878">I swear on my life.</font>

666
01:08:16.043 --> 01:08:17.203
<font color="#787878">I believe you.</font>

667
01:08:23.217 --> 01:08:24.946
<font color="#787878">Avada Kedavra!</font>

668
01:08:39.600 --> 01:08:41.090
<font color="#787878">I thought it had stopped.</font>

669
01:08:43.004 --> 01:08:45.438
<font color="#787878">You can't keep letting him in, Harry.</font>

670
01:08:47.508 --> 01:08:50.443
<font color="#787878">You-Know-Who has found Gregorovitch.</font>

671
01:08:50.745 --> 01:08:52.303
<font color="#787878">The wandmaker?</font>

672
01:08:52.480 --> 01:08:57.008
<font color="#787878">He wants something
that Gregorovitch used to have....</font>

673
01:08:57.184 --> 01:08:58.651
<font color="#787878">....but I don't know what.</font>

674
01:08:58.819 --> 01:09:04.815
<font color="#787878">But he wants it desperately. I mean, it's as if his life depends on it.</font>

675
01:09:06.360 --> 01:09:07.884
<font color="#787878">Don't.</font>

676
01:09:08.062 --> 01:09:10.257
<font color="#787878">~ It comforts him.
~ It sets my teeth on edge.</font>

677
01:09:10.431 --> 01:09:12.661
<font color="#787878">What's he expecting to hear, good news?</font>

678
01:09:12.833 --> 01:09:15.700
<font color="#787878">~ who long expected it,
the fall of the Ministry was shocking.</font>

679
01:09:15.870 --> 01:09:18.236
<font color="#787878">I think he just hopes
he doesn't hear bad news.</font>

680
01:09:18.406 --> 01:09:20.340
<font color="#787878">We promise
to remain your eyes and ears-</font>

681
01:09:20.508 --> 01:09:21.941
<font color="#787878">How long before he can travel?</font>

682
01:09:22.109 --> 01:09:25.306
<font color="#787878">~ bringing you news when we can, from wherever we can.</font>

683
01:09:25.479 --> 01:09:26.776
<font color="#787878">I'm doing everything I can.</font>

684
01:09:26.947 --> 01:09:28.471
<font color="#787878">You're not doing enough!</font>

685
01:09:31.218 --> 01:09:33.243
<font color="#787878">Take it off.</font>

686
01:09:34.021 --> 01:09:36.581
<font color="#787878">I said, take it off now.</font>

687
01:09:47.601 --> 01:09:50.331
<font color="#787878">~ Better?
~ Loads.</font>

688
01:09:54.041 --> 01:09:56.305
<font color="#787878">We'll take it in turns, okay?</font>

689
01:10:25.372 --> 01:10:28.739
<font color="#787878">Finch does admit
his invention currently has one short.</font>

690
01:10:28.909 --> 01:10:30.376
<font color="#787878">And now, other news:</font>

691
01:10:30.544 --> 01:10:33.809
<font color="#787878">Severus Snape, newly-appointed headmaster of Hogwarts....</font>

692
01:10:33.981 --> 01:10:37.747
<font color="#787878">....has decreed that all students must conform to the latest house rules.</font>

693
01:11:05.379 --> 01:11:09.816
<font color="#787878">Hogwarts bears little resemblance to the school under Dumbledore's leadership.</font>

694
01:11:09.984 --> 01:11:13.613
<font color="#787878">Snape's curriculum is severe, reflecting the wishes of the Dark Lord....</font>

695
01:11:14.455 --> 01:11:19.392
<font color="#787878">....and infractions are dealt with harshly by the two Death Eaters on staff.</font>

696
01:11:38.879 --> 01:11:40.210
<font color="#787878">What's that?</font>

697
01:11:49.490 --> 01:11:52.254
<font color="#787878">What's that smell?</font>

698
01:12:14.715 --> 01:12:16.740
<font color="#787878">~ What you doing?
~ It's heavy.</font>

699
01:12:16.917 --> 01:12:18.509
<font color="#787878">Oh, sorry. Do you want me to carry it?</font>

700
01:12:18.686 --> 01:12:21.621
<font color="#787878">~ Yeah, thank you.
~ Don't be ridiculous. Pick it up.</font>

701
01:12:23.190 --> 01:12:24.214
<font color="#787878">Numpty.</font>

702
01:12:29.330 --> 01:12:31.321
<font color="#787878">Snatchers.</font>

703
01:12:32.366 --> 01:12:34.800
<font color="#787878">Good to know your enchantments work.</font>

704
01:12:39.840 --> 01:12:43.469
<font color="#787878">He could smell it. My perfume.</font>

705
01:12:45.679 --> 01:12:47.738
<font color="#787878">I've told you....</font>

706
01:12:48.215 --> 01:12:50.046
<font color="#787878">....Ron isn't strong enough to Apparate.</font>

707
01:12:50.217 --> 01:12:53.948
<font color="#787878">Well, then, we'll go on foot.</font>

708
01:12:54.755 --> 01:12:59.692
<font color="#787878">And next time, Hermione, as much as I like your perfume, just don't wear any.</font>

709
01:13:04.598 --> 01:13:08.466
<font color="#787878">And now for the names
of missing witches and wizards.</font>

710
01:13:09.336 --> 01:13:11.497
<font color="#787878">These are confirmed.</font>

711
01:13:12.339 --> 01:13:15.706
<font color="#787878">Thankfully, the list is short today.</font>

712
01:13:16.443 --> 01:13:18.502
<font color="#787878">Jason and Alison Denbright.</font>

713
01:13:19.380 --> 01:13:20.404
<font color="#787878">Oh. Thank you.</font>

714
01:13:20.581 --> 01:13:24.312
<font color="#787878">Bella, Jake, Charlie, and Madge Farley.</font>

715
01:13:24.652 --> 01:13:25.676
<font color="#787878">Joe Laurie.</font>

716
01:13:26.987 --> 01:13:29.581
<font color="#787878">Eleanor Sarah Gibbs.</font>

717
01:13:30.758 --> 01:13:34.057
<font color="#787878">Harry and Bronwyn Trigg.</font>

718
01:13:35.696 --> 01:13:38.722
<font color="#787878">Rob and Ellie Dowson.</font>

719
01:13:39.833 --> 01:13:42.358
<font color="#787878">Georgia Clark-Day.</font>

720
01:13:42.937 --> 01:13:45.462
<font color="#787878">Joshua Flexson.</font>

721
01:13:45.873 --> 01:13:47.363
<font color="#787878">George Coutas.</font>

722
01:13:48.509 --> 01:13:51.342
<font color="#787878">Gabriella and Emily Mather.</font>

723
01:13:52.379 --> 01:13:55.473
<font color="#787878">Jacob and Mimi Erland.</font>

724
01:13:56.550 --> 01:13:58.040
<font color="#787878">William and Brian Gallagher.</font>

725
01:13:58.218 --> 01:14:00.652
<font color="#787878">He doesn't know
what he's doing, does he?</font>

726
01:14:03.490 --> 01:14:05.390
<font color="#787878">None of us do.</font>

727
01:14:07.962 --> 01:14:10.726
<font color="#787878">Toby and Olivia Gleaves.</font>

728
01:14:11.598 --> 01:14:14.226
<font color="#787878">Katie and James Killick.</font>

729
01:14:14.401 --> 01:14:16.926
<font color="#787878">Elsie Valentine Schroeder.</font>

730
01:14:17.972 --> 01:14:20.065
<font color="#787878">Jennifer Winston.</font>

731
01:14:20.240 --> 01:14:23.334
<font color="#787878">Tamsin and lola Hillicker.</font>

732
01:14:24.545 --> 01:14:25.569
<font color="#787878">Scarlet and Kitty Sharp.</font>

733
01:14:44.618 --> 01:14:46.449
<font color="#787878">Oh, my God.</font>

734
01:14:46.821 --> 01:14:48.448
<font color="#787878">What?</font>

735
01:14:49.023 --> 01:14:51.048
<font color="#787878">I'll tell you in a minute.</font>

736
01:14:51.592 --> 01:14:54.288
<font color="#787878">Maybe you could tell me now.</font>

737
01:14:54.662 --> 01:14:57.688
<font color="#787878">The sword of Gryffindor,
it's goblin-made.</font>

738
01:14:57.865 --> 01:14:58.957
<font color="#787878">Brilliant.</font>

739
01:15:00.034 --> 01:15:02.434
<font color="#787878">No, you don't understand.</font>

740
01:15:02.770 --> 01:15:05.136
<font color="#787878">Dirt and rust have no effect on the blade.</font>

741
01:15:06.140 --> 01:15:09.507
<font color="#787878">It only takes in
that which makes it stronger.</font>

742
01:15:09.910 --> 01:15:11.275
<font color="#787878">Okay.</font>

743
01:15:11.445 --> 01:15:14.937
<font color="#787878">Harry, you've already destroyed one Horcrux, right?</font>

744
01:15:15.116 --> 01:15:17.380
<font color="#787878">Tom Riddle's diary
in the Chamber of Secrets.</font>

745
01:15:17.551 --> 01:15:20.452
<font color="#787878">With a Basilisk fang.
If you tell me you've got one of those....</font>

746
01:15:20.621 --> 01:15:24.079
<font color="#787878">~ ....in that bloody beaded bag of yours....
~ Don't you see?</font>

747
01:15:24.258 --> 01:15:27.989
<font color="#787878">In the Chamber of Secrets, you stabbed the Basilisk with the sword of Gryffindor.</font>

748
01:15:28.162 --> 01:15:31.689
<font color="#787878">Its blade is impregnated
with Basilisk venom.</font>

749
01:15:31.866 --> 01:15:33.959
<font color="#787878">It only takes in
that which makes it stronger.</font>

750
01:15:34.135 --> 01:15:37.298
<font color="#787878">~ Exactly, which is why--
~ It can destroy Horcruxes.</font>

751
01:15:37.471 --> 01:15:39.735
<font color="#787878">That's why Dumbledore left it to you in his will.</font>

752
01:15:39.907 --> 01:15:44.310
<font color="#787878">You are brilliant, Hermione. Truly.</font>

753
01:15:44.478 --> 01:15:48.539
<font color="#787878">Actually, I'm highly logical, which allows me to look past extraneous detail....</font>

754
01:15:48.716 --> 01:15:51.207
<font color="#787878">....and perceive clearly
that which others overlook.</font>

755
01:15:51.385 --> 01:15:54.081
<font color="#787878">Yeah, there's only one problem, of course.</font>

756
01:15:59.460 --> 01:16:01.587
<font color="#787878">The sword was stolen.</font>

757
01:16:02.997 --> 01:16:05.522
<font color="#787878">Yeah, I'm still here.</font>

758
01:16:06.033 --> 01:16:10.163
<font color="#787878">But you two carry on.
Don't let me spoil the fun.</font>

759
01:16:11.539 --> 01:16:15.532
<font color="#787878">~ What's wrong?
~ Wrong? Nothing's wrong.</font>

760
01:16:15.709 --> 01:16:17.609
<font color="#787878">Not according to you, anyway.</font>

761
01:16:17.778 --> 01:16:21.407
<font color="#787878">Look, if you've got something to say, don't be shy. Spit it out.</font>

762
01:16:21.782 --> 01:16:25.081
<font color="#787878">All right, I'll spit it out. But don't expect me to be grateful....</font>

763
01:16:25.252 --> 01:16:27.777
<font color="#787878">....because there's another damn thing we've gotta find.</font>

764
01:16:27.955 --> 01:16:30.219
<font color="#787878">I thought you knew
what you signed up for.</font>

765
01:16:30.724 --> 01:16:32.589
<font color="#787878">Yeah. I thought I did too.</font>

766
01:16:32.760 --> 01:16:35.786
<font color="#787878">Well then, I'm sorry,
but I don't quite understand.</font>

767
01:16:35.963 --> 01:16:39.421
<font color="#787878">What part of this isn't living up to your expectations?</font>

768
01:16:39.600 --> 01:16:41.864
<font color="#787878">Did you think we were gonna be staying in a hotel?</font>

769
01:16:42.036 --> 01:16:45.301
<font color="#787878">Finding a Horcrux every other day? Thought you'd be back by Christmas?</font>

770
01:16:45.472 --> 01:16:47.303
<font color="#787878">I just thought, after all this time....</font>

