01:43:48.394 --> 01:43:52.490
<font color="#787878">~ Don't think this changes anything.
~ Oh, of course not.</font>

964
01:43:52.665 --> 01:43:55.930
<font color="#787878">I only just destroyed a bloody Horcrux. Why would that change anything?</font>

965
01:43:56.101 --> 01:44:00.162
<font color="#787878">Look, I wanted to come back as soon as I left.</font>

966
01:44:00.339 --> 01:44:03.775
<font color="#787878">~ I just didn't know how to find you.
~ Yeah, how did you find us?</font>

967
01:44:03.943 --> 01:44:07.003
<font color="#787878">With this. It doesn't just turn off lights.</font>

968
01:44:07.179 --> 01:44:12.082
<font color="#787878">I don't know how it works, but Christmas morning I was sleeping in this little pub....</font>

969
01:44:12.251 --> 01:44:14.685
<font color="#787878">....keeping away from some Snatchers....</font>

970
01:44:15.120 --> 01:44:16.382
<font color="#787878">....and I heard it.</font>

971
01:44:16.789 --> 01:44:18.222
<font color="#787878">It?</font>

972
01:44:19.558 --> 01:44:21.492
<font color="#787878">A voice....</font>

973
01:44:23.095 --> 01:44:24.289
<font color="#787878">....your voice, Hermione....</font>

974
01:44:25.464 --> 01:44:27.091
<font color="#787878">....coming out of it.</font>

975
01:44:27.266 --> 01:44:31.100
<font color="#787878">~ And what exactly did I say, may I ask?
~ My name.</font>

976
01:44:31.704 --> 01:44:33.729
<font color="#787878">Just my name.</font>

977
01:44:34.506 --> 01:44:36.599
<font color="#787878">Like a whisper.</font>

978
01:44:38.577 --> 01:44:44.573
<font color="#787878">So I took it, clicked it,
and this tiny ball of light appeared.</font>

979
01:44:45.050 --> 01:44:46.483
<font color="#787878">And I knew.</font>

980
01:44:47.052 --> 01:44:51.682
<font color="#787878">And sure enough, it floated toward me, the ball of light....</font>

981
01:44:53.392 --> 01:44:57.590
<font color="#787878">....went right to my chest, straight through me. Right here.</font>

982
01:44:58.797 --> 01:45:02.790
<font color="#787878">And I knew it was gonna take me where I needed to go, so I Disapparated....</font>

983
01:45:02.968 --> 01:45:05.232
<font color="#787878">....and came to this hillside.</font>

984
01:45:05.771 --> 01:45:08.296
<font color="#787878">It was dark. I had no idea where I was.</font>

985
01:45:08.841 --> 01:45:11.674
<font color="#787878">I just hoped
that one of you would show yourself.</font>

986
01:45:12.578 --> 01:45:14.102
<font color="#787878">And you did.</font>

987
01:45:31.530 --> 01:45:34.431
<font color="#787878">I've always liked these flames Hermione makes.</font>

988
01:45:38.470 --> 01:45:41.030
<font color="#787878">How long do you reckon
she'll stay mad at me?</font>

989
01:45:42.574 --> 01:45:45.907
<font color="#787878">Well, just keep talking about that little ball of light touching your heart....</font>

990
01:45:46.078 --> 01:45:47.511
<font color="#787878">....and she'll come round.</font>

991
01:45:47.680 --> 01:45:50.410
<font color="#787878">It was true. Every word.</font>

992
01:45:52.217 --> 01:45:54.583
<font color="#787878">This is gonna sound crazy....</font>

993
01:45:55.054 --> 01:45:59.423
<font color="#787878">....but I think that's why Dumbledore left it to me, the Deluminator.</font>

994
01:45:59.925 --> 01:46:04.919
<font color="#787878">I think he knew that somehow I'd need it to find my way back, and she'd lead me.</font>

995
01:46:07.800 --> 01:46:10.530
<font color="#787878">Bloody hell, I just realized, you need a wand, don't you?</font>

996
01:46:10.703 --> 01:46:13.194
<font color="#787878">~ Yeah.
~ I've got one here.</font>

997
01:46:13.472 --> 01:46:16.066
<font color="#787878">It's a blackthorn. Ten inches.</font>

998
01:46:16.241 --> 01:46:19.836
<font color="#787878">Nothing special, but I reckon it'll do.</font>

999
01:46:20.279 --> 01:46:23.077
<font color="#787878">Took if off a Snatcher
a couple of weeks ago.</font>

1000
01:46:23.582 --> 01:46:27.416
<font color="#787878">Don't tell Hermione this,
but they're a bit dim, Snatchers.</font>

1001
01:46:27.686 --> 01:46:30.621
<font color="#787878">This one was definitely part troll, the smell of him.</font>

1002
01:46:30.789 --> 01:46:31.813
<font color="#787878">Engorgio.</font>

1003
01:46:31.991 --> 01:46:34.152
<font color="#787878">~ Reducio!
What's going on in there?</font>

1004
01:46:34.326 --> 01:46:35.588
<font color="#787878">~ Nothing.
~ Nothing.</font>

1005
01:46:37.963 --> 01:46:39.590
<font color="#787878">We need to talk.</font>

1006
01:46:40.399 --> 01:46:41.593
<font color="#787878">Yeah, all right.</font>

1007
01:46:48.574 --> 01:46:52.101
<font color="#787878">~ I want to go see Xenophilius Lovegood.
~ Sorry?</font>

1008
01:46:53.879 --> 01:46:55.506
<font color="#787878">See this?</font>

1009
01:46:55.681 --> 01:46:59.549
<font color="#787878">It's a letter Dumbledore wrote to Grindelwald. Look at the signature.</font>

1010
01:47:00.786 --> 01:47:02.981
<font color="#787878">It's the mark again.</font>

1011
01:47:03.922 --> 01:47:06.049
<font color="#787878">It keeps cropping up.</font>

1012
01:47:06.225 --> 01:47:10.594
<font color="#787878">In Beedle the Bard,
in the graveyard in Godric's Hollow.</font>

1013
01:47:11.430 --> 01:47:13.295
<font color="#787878">It was there too.</font>

1014
01:47:13.465 --> 01:47:17.060
<font color="#787878">~ Where?
~ Outside Gregorovitch's Wand Shop.</font>

1015
01:47:17.503 --> 01:47:18.731
<font color="#787878">But what does it mean?</font>

1016
01:47:18.904 --> 01:47:23.705
<font color="#787878">Look, you've got no idea where the next Horcrux is, and neither do I....</font>

1017
01:47:25.411 --> 01:47:28.346
<font color="#787878">....but this, this means something.</font>

1018
01:47:28.680 --> 01:47:32.081
<font color="#787878">~ I'm sure of it.
~ Yeah. Hermione's right.</font>

1019
01:47:33.118 --> 01:47:35.211
<font color="#787878">We ought to see Lovegood.</font>

1020
01:47:35.721 --> 01:47:39.452
<font color="#787878">Let's vote on it. Those in favor?</font>

1021
01:48:03.282 --> 01:48:05.910
<font color="#787878">You're not still mad at him, are you?</font>

1022
01:48:06.218 --> 01:48:08.482
<font color="#787878">I'm always mad at him.</font>

1023
01:48:11.256 --> 01:48:12.746
<font color="#787878">Luna.</font>

1024
01:48:12.925 --> 01:48:14.620
<font color="#787878">Luna.</font>

1025
01:48:22.301 --> 01:48:25.134
<font color="#787878">"Keep off the dirigible plums."</font>

1026
01:48:34.179 --> 01:48:36.875
<font color="#787878">What is it? Who are you?</font>

1027
01:48:37.182 --> 01:48:38.206
<font color="#787878">What do you want?</font>

1028
01:48:38.383 --> 01:48:42.979
<font color="#787878">Hello, Mr. Lovegood. I'm Harry Potter. We met a few months ago.</font>

1029
01:48:46.992 --> 01:48:48.892
<font color="#787878">Could we come in?</font>

1030
01:48:52.664 --> 01:48:55.258
<font color="#787878">~ Where is Luna?
~ Luna?</font>

1031
01:48:56.535 --> 01:48:58.503
<font color="#787878">She'll be along.</font>

1032
01:49:12.017 --> 01:49:14.076
<font color="#787878">So how can I help you, Mr. Potter?</font>

1033
01:49:14.920 --> 01:49:17.946
<font color="#787878">Well, actually....</font>

1034
01:49:18.957 --> 01:49:23.485
<font color="#787878">It was about something you were wearing round your neck at the wedding. A symbol.</font>

1035
01:49:25.030 --> 01:49:26.930
<font color="#787878">You mean this?</font>

1036
01:49:27.332 --> 01:49:28.924
<font color="#787878">Yes.</font>

1037
01:49:29.234 --> 01:49:31.099
<font color="#787878">That exactly.</font>

1038
01:49:31.770 --> 01:49:35.729
<font color="#787878">What we've wondered is, what is it?</font>

1039
01:49:35.908 --> 01:49:37.739
<font color="#787878">What is it?</font>

1040
01:49:37.910 --> 01:49:40.879
<font color="#787878">Well, it's the sign of the Deathly Hallows, of course.</font>

1041
01:49:41.046 --> 01:49:42.138
<font color="#787878">~ The what?
~ The what?</font>

1042
01:49:42.314 --> 01:49:44.373
<font color="#787878">The Deathly Hallows.</font>

1043
01:49:44.550 --> 01:49:47.644
<font color="#787878">I assume you're all familiar with "The Tale of the Three Brothers."</font>

1044
01:49:47.819 --> 01:49:49.309
<font color="#787878">~ Yes.
~ No.</font>

1045
01:49:54.660 --> 01:49:56.423
<font color="#787878">I have it in here.</font>

1046
01:50:07.673 --> 01:50:09.300
<font color="#787878">"There were once three brothers....</font>

1047
01:50:09.474 --> 01:50:13.877
<font color="#787878">....who were traveling along a lonely, winding road at twilight."</font>

1048
01:50:14.046 --> 01:50:16.776
<font color="#787878">Midnight. Mom always said "midnight."</font>

1049
01:50:21.787 --> 01:50:25.655
<font color="#787878">But "twilight's" fine. Better, actually.</font>

1050
01:50:27.926 --> 01:50:29.791
<font color="#787878">Do you want to read it?</font>

1051
01:50:29.962 --> 01:50:32.157
<font color="#787878">No. It's fine.</font>

1052
01:50:34.066 --> 01:50:36.000
<font color="#787878">"There were once three brothers....</font>

1053
01:50:36.168 --> 01:50:41.367
<font color="#787878">....who were traveling along a lonely, winding road at twilight.</font>

1054
01:50:43.242 --> 01:50:48.544
<font color="#787878">In time, the brothers reached a river too treacherous to pass.</font>

1055
01:50:48.880 --> 01:50:50.745
<font color="#787878">But being learned in the magical arts....</font>

1056
01:50:50.916 --> 01:50:56.081
<font color="#787878">....the three brothers simply waved their wands and made a bridge.</font>

1057
01:50:57.422 --> 01:50:59.515
<font color="#787878">Before they could cross, however....</font>

1058
01:50:59.691 --> 01:51:03.787
<font color="#787878">....they found their path blocked by a hooded figure.</font>

1059
01:51:04.062 --> 01:51:07.930
<font color="#787878">It was Death, and he felt cheated.</font>

1060
01:51:08.100 --> 01:51:11.160
<font color="#787878">Cheated because travelers would normally drown in the river.</font>

1061
01:51:11.336 --> 01:51:13.395
<font color="#787878">But Death was cunning.</font>

1062
01:51:14.039 --> 01:51:17.031
<font color="#787878">He pretended to congratulate the three brothers on their magic....</font>

1063
01:51:17.209 --> 01:51:22.476
<font color="#787878">....and said that each had earned a prize for having been clever enough to evade him.</font>

1064
01:51:23.048 --> 01:51:27.610
<font color="#787878">The oldest asked for a wand more powerful than any in existence.</font>

1065
01:51:27.786 --> 01:51:32.382
<font color="#787878">So Death fashioned him one
from an elder tree that stood nearby.</font>

1066
01:51:33.792 --> 01:51:38.092
<font color="#787878">The second brother decided he wanted to humiliate Death even further....</font>

1067
01:51:38.263 --> 01:51:42.700
<font color="#787878">....and asked for the power to recall loved ones from the grave.</font>

1068
01:51:43.135 --> 01:51:47.435
<font color="#787878">So Death plucked a stone from the river and offered it to him.</font>

1069
01:51:48.173 --> 01:51:52.132
<font color="#787878">Finally,
Death turned to the third brother.</font>

1070
01:51:53.345 --> 01:51:54.778
<font color="#787878">A humble man....</font>

1071
01:51:54.946 --> 01:51:59.144
<font color="#787878">....he asked for something that would allow him to go forth from that place....</font>

1072
01:51:59.318 --> 01:52:02.481
<font color="#787878">....without being followed by Death.</font>

1073
01:52:03.588 --> 01:52:09.458
<font color="#787878">And so it was that Death reluctantly handed over his own Cloak of Invisibility.</font>

1074
01:52:12.831 --> 01:52:15.766
<font color="#787878">The first brother traveled
to a distant village....</font>

1075
01:52:15.934 --> 01:52:18.027
<font color="#787878">....where, with the Elder Wand in hand....</font>

1076
01:52:18.203 --> 01:52:21.969
<font color="#787878">....he killed a wizard
with whom he had once quarreled.</font>

1077
01:52:24.176 --> 01:52:27.703
<font color="#787878">Drunk with the power
that the Elder Wand had given him....</font>

1078
01:52:27.879 --> 01:52:30.973
<font color="#787878">....he bragged of his invincibility.</font>

1079
01:52:33.985 --> 01:52:37.443
<font color="#787878">But that night,
another wizard stole the wand....</font>

1080
01:52:37.622 --> 01:52:40.750
<font color="#787878">....and slit the brother's throat for good measure.</font>

1081
01:52:40.959 --> 01:52:44.395
<font color="#787878">And so Death took the first brother for his own.</font>

1082
01:52:45.130 --> 01:52:47.098
<font color="#787878">The second brother journeyed to his home....</font>

1083
01:52:47.265 --> 01:52:50.234
<font color="#787878">....where he took the stone and turned it thrice in hand.</font>

1084
01:52:50.402 --> 01:52:54.862
<font color="#787878">To his delight, the girl he'd once hoped to marry before her untimely death....</font>

1085
01:52:55.040 --> 01:52:57.406
<font color="#787878">....appeared before him.</font>

1086
01:52:57.909 --> 01:53:03.211
<font color="#787878">Yet, soon she turned sad and cold for she did not belong in the mortal world.</font>

1087
01:53:03.382 --> 01:53:05.009
<font color="#787878">Driven mad with hopeless longing....</font>

1088
01:53:05.183 --> 01:53:08.482
<font color="#787878">....the second brother killed himself so as to join her.</font>

1089
01:53:09.688 --> 01:53:12.782
<font color="#787878">And so Death took the second brother.</font>

1090
01:53:12.958 --> 01:53:14.585
<font color="#787878">As for the third brother....</font>

1091
01:53:14.760 --> 01:53:18.992
<font color="#787878">....Death searched for many years but was never able to find him.</font>

1092
01:53:19.164 --> 01:53:22.065
<font color="#787878">Only when he attained a great age did the youngest brother....</font>

1093
01:53:22.234 --> 01:53:26.500
<font color="#787878">....shed the Cloak of Invisibility and give it to his son.</font>

1094
01:53:27.739 --> 01:53:31.869
<font color="#787878">He then greeted Death as an old friend and went with him gladly....</font>

1095
01:53:32.043 --> 01:53:35.206
<font color="#787878">....departing this life as equals."</font>

1096
01:53:37.282 --> 01:53:41.776
<font color="#787878">So there you are.
Those are the Deathly Hallows.</font>

1097
01:53:43.188 --> 01:53:46.248
<font color="#787878">I'm sorry, sir.
I still don't quite understand.</font>

1098
01:53:51.863 --> 01:53:53.956
<font color="#787878">Where's that pen I had?</font>

1099
01:54:04.943 --> 01:54:06.205
<font color="#787878">The Elder Wand.</font>

1100
01:54:07.345 --> 01:54:11.008
<font color="#787878">The most powerful wand ever made.</font>

1101
01:54:21.393 --> 01:54:23.691
<font color="#787878">The Resurrection Stone.</font>

1102
01:54:34.573 --> 01:54:38.339
<font color="#787878">The Cloak of Invisibility.</font>

1103
01:54:40.378 --> 01:54:43.506
<font color="#787878">Together, they make the Deathly Hallows.</font>

1104
01:54:43.782 --> 01:54:49.243
<font color="#787878">Together, they make one
master of Death.</font>

1105
01:54:54.459 --> 01:54:58.122
<font color="#787878">That mark was on a grave
in Godric's Hollow.</font>

1106
01:54:59.231 --> 01:55:01.859
<font color="#787878">Uh, Mr. Lovegood,
does the Peverell Family....</font>

1107
01:55:02.033 --> 01:55:03.864
<font color="#787878">....have anything to do
with the Deathly Hallows?</font>

1108
01:55:04.035 --> 01:55:06.868
<font color="#787878">Uh-- Uh--</font>

1109
01:55:07.038 --> 01:55:10.804
<font color="#787878">Ignotus-- Excuse me. --and his brothers, Cadmus and Antioch....</font>

1110
01:55:10.976 --> 01:55:13.638
<font color="#787878">....are thought to be the original owners of the Hallows....</font>

1111
01:55:13.812 --> 01:55:18.681
<font color="#787878">....and therefore the inspiration for the story. Uh-- Uh--</font>

1112
01:55:18.850 --> 01:55:21.341
<font color="#787878">But your tea's gone cold.</font>

1113
01:55:22.554 --> 01:55:24.545
<font color="#787878">I'll be right back.</font>

1114
01:55:24.723 --> 01:55:26.588
<font color="#787878">Let's go down here.</font>

1115
01:55:28.460 --> 01:55:29.950
<font color="#787878">Let's get out of here.</font>

1116
01:55:30.128 --> 01:55:32.995
<font color="#787878">I'm not drinking any more of that stuff, hot or cold.</font>

1117
01:55:39.304 --> 01:55:41.272
<font color="#787878">Thank you, sir.</font>

1118
01:55:42.173 --> 01:55:45.199
<font color="#787878">~ You forgot the water.
~ Water?</font>

1119
01:55:45.377 --> 01:55:46.810
<font color="#787878">For the tea.</font>

1120
01:55:46.978 --> 01:55:49.538
<font color="#787878">Did--? Did I?</font>

1121
01:55:51.483 --> 01:55:53.644
<font color="#787878">How silly of me.</font>

1122
01:55:55.253 --> 01:55:57.517
<font color="#787878">It's no matter.
We really should be going anyway.</font>

1123
01:55:57.689 --> 01:55:59.748
<font color="#787878">No, you can't!</font>

1124
01:56:03.962 --> 01:56:05.657
<font color="#787878">Sir?</font>

1125
01:56:13.038 --> 01:56:15.632
<font color="#787878">You're my only hope.</font>

1126
01:56:19.511 --> 01:56:23.880
<font color="#787878">They were angry, you see,
about what I'd been writing.</font>

1127
01:56:26.918 --> 01:56:29.045
<font color="#787878">So they took her.</font>

1128
01:56:30.522 --> 01:56:33.286
<font color="#787878">They took my Luna.</font>

1129
01:56:34.993 --> 01:56:36.620
<font color="#787878">My Luna.</font>

1130
01:56:49.107 --> 01:56:52.008
<font color="#787878">But it's really you they want.</font>

1131
01:56:54.245 --> 01:56:56.304
<font color="#787878">Who took her, sir?</font>

1132
01:57:01.453 --> 01:57:02.715
<font color="#787878">Voldemort.</font>

1133
01:57:13.365 --> 01:57:15.663
<font color="#787878">Stop! I've got him!</font>

1134
01:57:32.951 --> 01:57:36.853
<font color="#787878">That treacherous little bleeder. Is there no one we can trust?</font>

1135
01:57:37.022 --> 01:57:39.320
<font color="#787878">They kidnapped her
because he supported me.</font>

1136
01:57:39.491 --> 01:57:41.618
<font color="#787878">He was just desperate.</font>

1137
01:57:42.160 --> 01:57:44.355
<font color="#787878">I'll do the enchantments.</font>

1138
01:57:56.041 --> 01:57:57.474
<font color="#787878">Hello, beautiful.</font>

1139
01:58:02.947 --> 01:58:06.576
<font color="#787878">Well, don't hang about, snatch them.</font>

1140
01:59:17.822 --> 01:59:19.312
<font color="#787878">Harry.</font>

1141
01:59:19.491 --> 01:59:22.460
<font color="#787878">Tell me, Grindelwald.
Tell me where it is.</font>

1142
01:59:23.061 --> 01:59:27.122
<font color="#787878">Grindelwald. Grindelwald. Grindelwald.</font>

1143
01:59:27.866 --> 01:59:31.324
<font color="#787878">Hello, Tom.
I knew you would come one day....</font>

1144
01:59:31.803 --> 01:59:35.762
<font color="#787878">....but surely you must know I no longer have what you seek.</font>

1145
01:59:36.407 --> 01:59:39.433
<font color="#787878">~ Tell me, Grindelwald. Tell me where it is.
~ Ha-ha-ha.</font>

1146
01:59:39.611 --> 01:59:40.976
<font color="#787878">Tell me who possesses it.</font>

1147
01:59:41.179 --> 01:59:46.276
<font color="#787878">The Elder Wand lies with him, of course....</font>

1148
01:59:46.451 --> 01:59:48.715
<font color="#787878">....buried in the earth.</font>

1149
01:59:49.654 --> 01:59:50.985
<font color="#787878">Dumbledore.</font>

1150
02:00:00.031 --> 02:00:01.896
<font color="#787878">The Hallows exist....</font>

1151
02:00:02.066 --> 02:00:05.866
<font color="#787878">....but he's only after one of them, the last one. He knows where it is.</font>

1152
02:00:06.037 --> 02:00:09.871
<font color="#787878">He's gonna have it by the end of the night. You-Know-Who's found the Elder Wand.</font>

1153
02:00:10.041 --> 02:00:12.509
<font color="#787878">~ Don't touch her. Unh!
~ Leave him.</font>

1154
02:00:12.677 --> 02:00:13.939
<font color="#787878">Your boyfriend will get worse than that....</font>

1155
02:00:14.112 --> 02:00:15.238
<font color="#787878">Get off me.</font>

1156
02:00:15.413 --> 02:00:18.143
<font color="#787878">....if he doesn't learn to behave himself.</font>

1157
02:00:21.386 --> 02:00:22.876
<font color="#787878">What happened to you, ugly?</font>

1158
02:00:24.589 --> 02:00:26.454
<font color="#787878">No, not you.</font>

1159
02:00:27.859 --> 02:00:30.919
<font color="#787878">~ What's your name?
~ Dudley. Vernon Dudley.</font>

1160
02:00:31.095 --> 02:00:33.290
<font color="#787878">Check it.</font>

1161
02:00:34.899 --> 02:00:37.231
<font color="#787878">And you, my lovely....</font>

1162
02:00:40.538 --> 02:00:42.529
<font color="#787878">....what do they call you?</font>

1163
02:00:43.975 --> 02:00:48.036
<font color="#787878">Penelope Clearwater, half-blood.</font>

1164
02:00:51.149 --> 02:00:53.083
<font color="#787878">There's no Vernon Dudley on here.</font>

1165
02:00:54.152 --> 02:00:57.383
<font color="#787878">Did you hear that, ugly?
The list says you're lying.</font>

1166
02:00:57.555 --> 02:00:59.785
<font color="#787878">How come you don't want us
to know who you are?</font>

1167
02:00:59.958 --> 02:01:02.620
<font color="#787878">The list's wrong. I told you who I am.</font>

1168
02:01:18.576 --> 02:01:20.669
<font color="#787878">Change of plan.</font>

1169
02:01:21.746 --> 02:01:25.011
<font color="#787878">We're not taking this lot to the Ministry.</font>

1170
02:02:04.689 --> 02:02:08.318
<font color="#787878">Get Draco.</font>

1171
02:02:12.797 --> 02:02:14.355
<font color="#787878">Well?</font>

1172
02:02:17.468 --> 02:02:21.996
<font color="#787878">~ I can't be sure.
~ Draco. Look closely, son.</font>

1173
02:02:23.007 --> 02:02:28.070
<font color="#787878">If we are the ones
to hand Potter over to the Dark Lord....</font>

1174
02:02:28.246 --> 02:02:33.479
<font color="#787878">....everything would be forgiven. All would be as it was, you understand?</font>

1175
02:02:33.651 --> 02:02:37.781
<font color="#787878">Now, we won't be forgetting who actually caught him, I hope, Mr. Malfoy.</font>

1176
02:02:37.956 --> 02:02:40.390
<font color="#787878">You dare to
talk to me like that in my own house?</font>

1177
02:02:40.558 --> 02:02:42.355
<font color="#787878">Lucius.</font>

1178
02:02:45.263 --> 02:02:49.097
<font color="#787878">Don't be shy, sweetie. Come over.</font>

1179
02:02:50.601 --> 02:02:55.368
<font color="#787878">Now, if this isn't who we think it is, Draco, and we call him, he'll kill us all.</font>

1180
02:02:55.540 --> 02:02:58.338
<font color="#787878">We need to be absolutely sure.</font>

1181
02:02:58.643 --> 02:02:59.632
<font color="#787878">What's wrong with his face?</font>

1182
02:02:59.811 --> 02:03:01.540
<font color="#787878">Yes, what is wrong with his face?</font>

1183
02:03:01.713 --> 02:03:02.907
<font color="#787878">He came to us like that.</font>

1184
02:03:03.081 --> 02:03:05.049
<font color="#787878">Something he picked up in the forest, I reckon.</font>

1185
02:03:05.216 --> 02:03:08.913
<font color="#787878">Or ran into a Stinging Jinx. Was it you, dearie?</font>

1186
02:03:14.025 --> 02:03:16.789
<font color="#787878">Give me her wand.
We'll see what her last spell was.</font>

1187
02:03:18.062 --> 02:03:20.223
<font color="#787878">Ah. Got you.</font>

1188
02:03:24.035 --> 02:03:25.764
<font color="#787878">What is that?</font>

1189
02:03:27.705 --> 02:03:29.297
<font color="#787878">Where'd you get that from?</font>

1190
02:03:29.474 --> 02:03:32.966
<font color="#787878">It was in her bag when we searched her. Reckon it's mine now.</font>

1191
02:03:36.714 --> 02:03:38.045
<font color="#787878">Are you mad?</font>

1192
02:03:46.357 --> 02:03:49.190
<font color="#787878">Go! Get out!</font>

1193
02:03:54.832 --> 02:03:58.996
<font color="#787878">Cissy, put the boys in the cellar.</font>

1194
02:03:59.170 --> 02:04:04.540
<font color="#787878">I want to have a little conversation with this one, girl-to-girl.</font>

1195
02:04:13.584 --> 02:04:16.678
<font color="#787878">What are we gonna do?
We can't leave Hermione alone with her.</font>

1196
02:04:16.854 --> 02:04:18.219
<font color="#787878">Ron?</font>

1197
02:04:23.428 --> 02:04:24.986
<font color="#787878">Harry?</font>

1198
02:04:30.701 --> 02:04:32.259
<font color="#787878">Luna?</font>

1199
02:04:32.870 --> 02:04:37.034
<font color="#787878">That sword is meant to be in my vault at Gringotts. How did you get it?</font>

1200
02:04:37.208 --> 02:04:40.336
<font color="#787878">What else did you and your friends take from my vault?!</font>

1201
02:04:40.511 --> 02:04:45.881
<font color="#787878">I didn't take anything. Please. I didn't take anything.</font>

1202
02:04:46.050 --> 02:04:47.574
<font color="#787878">I don't believe it.</font>

1203
02:04:53.157 --> 02:04:54.249
<font color="#787878">We have to do something.</font>

1204
02:04:54.425 --> 02:04:58.452
<font color="#787878">There's no way out of here. We've tried everything. It's enchanted.</font>

1205
02:04:58.629 --> 02:05:01.325
<font color="#787878">~ Please! please!
~ Shut up!</font>

1206
02:05:01.499 --> 02:05:03.296
<font color="#787878">You're bleeding, Harry.</font>

1207
02:05:03.468 --> 02:05:05.493
<font color="#787878">That's a curious thing
to keep in your sock.</font>

1208
02:05:14.745 --> 02:05:15.871
<font color="#787878">Help us.</font>

1209
02:05:21.652 --> 02:05:23.552
<font color="#787878">~ Let her go.
~ Shut up. Get back.</font>

1210
02:05:24.889 --> 02:05:29.087
<font color="#787878">You, goblin, come with me.</font>

1211
02:05:48.746 --> 02:05:50.236
<font color="#787878">~ Aah!
~ Dobby?</font>

1212
02:05:51.115 --> 02:05:52.514
<font color="#787878">What are you doing here?</font>

1213
02:05:52.683 --> 02:05:54.947
<font color="#787878">Dobby has come to rescue
Harry Potter, of course.</font>

1214
02:05:55.119 --> 02:05:57.587
<font color="#787878">Dobby will always be there
for Harry Potter.</font>

1215
02:05:57.755 --> 02:06:01.350
<font color="#787878">You can Apparate in and out of this room? Could you take us with you?</font>

1216
02:06:01.526 --> 02:06:03.289
<font color="#787878">Of course, sir. I'm an elf.</font>

1217
02:06:04.095 --> 02:06:05.960
<font color="#787878">Works for me.</font>

1218
02:06:06.197 --> 02:06:08.563
<font color="#787878">Dobby, I want you to take Luna and Mr. Ollivander--</font>

1219
02:06:08.733 --> 02:06:11.167
<font color="#787878">Shell Cottage
on the outskirts of Tinworth.</font>

1220
02:06:11.536 --> 02:06:12.560
<font color="#787878">Trust me.</font>

1221
02:06:13.371 --> 02:06:14.804
<font color="#787878">Whenever you're ready, sir.</font>

1222
02:06:15.506 --> 02:06:18.202
<font color="#787878">Sir? I like her very much.</font>

1223
02:06:23.147 --> 02:06:26.446
<font color="#787878">Meet me at the top of the stairs in 10 seconds.</font>

1224
02:06:35.526 --> 02:06:37.289
<font color="#787878">Ow.</font>

1225
02:06:42.700 --> 02:06:44.930
<font color="#787878">Who gets his wand?</font>

1226
02:06:47.672 --> 02:06:51.665
<font color="#787878">I'm only going to
ask you once more, goblin.</font>

1227
02:06:51.842 --> 02:06:55.243
<font color="#787878">Think very, very carefully
before you answer.</font>

1228
02:06:55.613 --> 02:06:57.171
<font color="#787878">I don't know.</font>

1229
02:06:57.348 --> 02:07:00.545
<font color="#787878">You don't know?
Why weren't you doing your job?</font>

1230
02:07:00.718 --> 02:07:03.949
<font color="#787878">Who got into my vault?</font>

1231
02:07:05.223 --> 02:07:09.660
<font color="#787878">Who stole it? Who stole it? Well?</font>

1232
02:07:09.827 --> 02:07:13.854
<font color="#787878">When I was last in your vault, the sword was there.</font>

1233
02:07:16.634 --> 02:07:19.831
<font color="#787878">Oh, well then, perhaps
it just walked out on its own then.</font>

1234
02:07:20.004 --> 02:07:22.438
<font color="#787878">There is no place safer than Gringotts.</font>

1235
02:07:22.607 --> 02:07:24.040
<font color="#787878">Liar!</font>

1236
02:07:25.977 --> 02:07:29.378
<font color="#787878">Consider yourself lucky, goblin.</font>

1237
02:07:31.816 --> 02:07:35.217
<font color="#787878">The same won't be said for this one.</font>

1238
02:07:35.386 --> 02:07:37.149
<font color="#787878">Like hell.</font>

1239
02:07:37.888 --> 02:07:39.116
<font color="#787878">Expellliarmus!</font>

1240
02:07:40.558 --> 02:07:41.650
<font color="#787878">Stupefy.</font>

1241
02:07:45.796 --> 02:07:47.161
<font color="#787878">Stop!</font>

1242
02:07:48.332 --> 02:07:49.890
<font color="#787878">Drop your wands.</font>

1243
02:07:52.770 --> 02:07:53.794
<font color="#787878">I said, drop them!</font>

1244
02:07:55.306 --> 02:07:56.739
<font color="#787878">Pick them up, Draco, now.</font>

1245
02:07:57.608 --> 02:08:01.738
<font color="#787878">Well, well, well,
look what we have here.</font>

1246
02:08:03.347 --> 02:08:04.837
<font color="#787878">It's Harry Potter.</font>

1247
02:08:05.616 --> 02:08:11.987
<font color="#787878">He's all bright and shiny and new again, just in time for the Dark Lord.</font>

1248
02:08:12.156 --> 02:08:14.181
<font color="#787878">Call him.</font>

1249
02:08:17.928 --> 02:08:19.725
<font color="#787878">Call him.</font>

1250
02:08:54.932 --> 02:08:56.763
<font color="#787878">Stupefy!</font>

1251
02:08:57.535 --> 02:08:59.230
<font color="#787878">Stupid elf.</font>

1252
02:08:59.403 --> 02:09:02.429
<font color="#787878">~ You could've killed me.
~ Dobby never meant to kill.</font>

1253
02:09:02.606 --> 02:09:06.633
<font color="#787878">Dobby only meant to maim
or seriously injure.</font>

1254
02:09:08.946 --> 02:09:12.279
<font color="#787878">How dare you take a witch's wand?</font>

1255
02:09:12.450 --> 02:09:15.442
<font color="#787878">How dare you defy your masters?</font>

1256
02:09:15.619 --> 02:09:18.747
<font color="#787878">Dobby has no master.</font>

1257
02:09:18.923 --> 02:09:21.414
<font color="#787878">Dobby is a free elf.</font>

1258
02:09:21.592 --> 02:09:26.552
<font color="#787878">And Dobby has come
to save Harry Potter and his friends.</font>

1259
02:09:56.394 --> 02:09:58.055
<font color="#787878">Hermione.</font>

1260
02:09:58.229 --> 02:10:00.720
<font color="#787878">You're all right. We're safe.</font>

1261
02:10:00.898 --> 02:10:02.923
<font color="#787878">We're all safe.</font>

1262
02:10:03.801 --> 02:10:05.996
<font color="#787878">Harry Potter.</font>

1263
02:10:09.740 --> 02:10:11.571
<font color="#787878">Dobby.</font>

1264
02:10:22.086 --> 02:10:25.146
<font color="#787878">Dobby. No, just-- Hold on.</font>

1265
02:10:25.322 --> 02:10:29.656
<font color="#787878">Hold on. Look, just hold on, okay?</font>

1266
02:10:29.827 --> 02:10:31.886
<font color="#787878">We'll fix you.</font>

1267
02:10:32.329 --> 02:10:35.059
<font color="#787878">Hermione will have something.</font>

1268
02:10:35.232 --> 02:10:37.564
<font color="#787878">In your bag. Hermione?</font>

1269
02:10:39.203 --> 02:10:40.534
<font color="#787878">Hermione?</font>

1270
02:10:42.740 --> 02:10:45.868
<font color="#787878">What is it? Help me.</font>

1271
02:10:48.446 --> 02:10:51.574
<font color="#787878">Such a beautiful place....</font>

1272
02:10:53.751 --> 02:10:56.015
<font color="#787878">....to be with friends.</font>

1273
02:10:57.822 --> 02:11:03.226
<font color="#787878">Dobby is happy to be with his friend....</font>

1274
02:11:05.629 --> 02:11:08.063
<font color="#787878">....Harry Potter.</font>

1275
02:11:28.853 --> 02:11:31.253
<font color="#787878">We should close his eyes.</font>

1276
02:11:31.489 --> 02:11:33.514
<font color="#787878">Don't you think?</font>

1277
02:11:38.629 --> 02:11:40.028
<font color="#787878">There.</font>

1278
02:11:40.498 --> 02:11:42.932
<font color="#787878">Now he could be sleeping.</font>

1279
02:11:58.249 --> 02:12:00.308
<font color="#787878">I want to bury him.</font>

1280
02:12:01.352 --> 02:12:04.913
<font color="#787878">Properly. Without magic.</font>
